\mt1 Mak Osirizir Akar Aghuim 
\is1 Akar Faragha Zuim 
\ip Mak osirizir ak…®nafarim, an akar faragha itim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar God…®n Otarim Krais Iesus…®n akar aghuim…®n m…®ngarim.‚Äù 
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam e an gari, Iesus a gumazir ingangarir av…®ribar amuamin gavgavim ko ziam iti. Ez…® dughiar a gumazamizibar sure gamiziba, ko dughiar a duar kuraba batogheziba, ko dughiar a gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadaziba, e ak…®nafarim…®n aven eghaghanir kabar gara kamagh…®n fo, a gavgavir ekiam ko ziar ekiam iti. Iesus a kamagh…®n uab…® d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazibar Borim‚Äù. Egha a kamagh…®n m…®gei, a gumazamizibagh ivezasa, kamagh…®n a uab…® me bagha ovenge. A bizir kam bagha ize (10:45). 
\ip Mak Iesus…®n ingangarir av…®ribagh eghani. Egha a Iesus gumazamizibar sure gamizir akar av…®ribagh eghanizir puvat…®. Mak faragha Jon, Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim…®n ingangarim, ko Iesus…®n rurim, ko Satan a gifarazir eghaghanim…®n gun m…®gei. Ez…® g…®n e Iesus…®n garima, a gumazir os…®mt…®zir av…®riba ateribar apangkufi, egha men sure gami. Ez…® faragha suren gumaziba Iesus amir bizibar m…®ngaribagh fozir puvat…®. Egha me n…®m…®ra n…®m…®ra me g…®n dagh fofosi. 
\ip E uaghan Iesus…®n apanibar gari, me os…®mt…®zir av…®riba a gar…®si. Egha Mak Osirizir Akar Aghuir aboananaba, a Iesus aremegha egha ua d…®kavizir eghaghanim geghari. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Iesus, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n gun gumazamizibav k…®masa ize 
\mr (Sapta 1:1-3:6) 
\s1 Jon, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim, faragha izava Iesus…®n akam akuri 
\r (Matyu 3:1-12 ko Luk 3:1-9 ko 3:15-17 ko Jon 1:19-28) 
\p  
\v 1 Kar God…®n Otarim Krais Iesus…®n akar aghuim.  
\v 2 God fom…®ra uan akam, an akam inigha izir gumazim Aisaia gan…®ngi. An an osiriz…®ma, an ak…®nafarim…®n iti. Akar kamra kara. 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúIa oragh! K…® uan abuir gumazim amadaght…®ma, a faragh mang…®va 
\q2 n…® bagh tuavim ak…®ram.‚Äù 
\q1  
\v 3 ‚ÄúGumazir tiarir mam gumaziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n dia ghaze, 
\q2 ‚ÄòIa Ekiam bagh…®va tuaviba azen…®va, dar k…®r.‚Äô‚Äù 
\b  
\m  
\v 4 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma Jon izava gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikiava gumaziba ruava kamagh…®n akam akuri, ‚ÄúIa navibagh iraght…®ma k…® ia rueght…®ma God ian arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham.‚Äù  
\v 5 An akar kabav geima Judian Distrigh…®n itir nguibaba koma Jerusalem…®n itir gumazamiziba me bar izava uan arazir kurabar gun m…®geima a Jordan…®n d…®pam…®n me rue. 
\p  
\v 6 Jon, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim, ana as…®zim kamel…®n ar…®zibar ingarizir iniba ikeghava as…®zir inim uan ivariam ike. A inir kaba ikeghava odeziba ko ruarim…®n haniba api.\f + \ft (1:6) N…® kamel ko hanibar m…®ngaribagh foghs…®, ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f* 
\v 7 Ez…® an akam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan g…®n izamin gumazim an gavgavim guizbang…®ra nan gavgavim gafira. K…® an m…®ngarir puvat…®. K…® uaghan aviragh…®va an dagarir asuabar beniba f…®ran gavgaviba puvat…®.  
\v 8 K…® d…®pam…®n ia rue, eght…® a g…®n God…®n Duam…®n ia ruam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ruez…®ma g…®n Satan a gifarasa a gakaghori 
\r (Matyu 3:13-17; 4:1-11 ko Luk 3:21-22; 4:1-13) 
\p  
\v 9 Dughiar kam Iesus Galilin Distrigh…®n itir nguibam, Nasaret, ateghava Jon bagha izez…®ma, a Jordan…®n d…®pam…®n a rue.  
\v 10 Iesus d…®pam…®n aven ikegha azenan otivav…®ra ikia garima overiam kuiaghir…®z…®ma God…®n Duam bunbam…®n m…®n m…®ghegha a bagha izaghiri.  
\v 11 Ez…® tiarir mam God…®n Nguibam…®n ikiava kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúN…® nan Otarim. K…® guizbang…®ra n…® g…®fueghava n…® bagha bar akonge.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® God…®n Duam anemadaz…®ma a gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganim…®n ghu.  
\v 13 A ghugha, 40 plan dughiabar danganir kam…®n itima, Satan a gifarasa a gakaghori. A ruarim…®n itir as…®ziba ko ikia dar torim…®n itima, God…®n enselba an garava an akurvasi. 
\s1 Iesus faragha zuir suren gumazibar dei 
\r (Matyu 4:12-17 ko Luk 4:14-15 ko Matyu 4:18-22 ko Luk 5:1-11) 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® me Jon, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim, inigha kalabus gat…®z…®ma, Iesus g…®n Galilin ghugha God…®n akar aghuim akuri.  
\v 15 A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDughiam otogha g…®fa. God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam rogh…®ra ize. Ia navibagh iragh…®va n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n akar aghuim…®n ik…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Dughiar mam Iesus Galilin d…®par m…®riam…®n ghuava Saimon uan dozim Andru ko aning…®n garima, aning osiriba baghava uan iver ekiaba kuri. Aning osiriba isa dagh ivezir gumazimning.  
\v 17 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua nan g…®n iz…®t…®ma k…® guan akakaght…®ma, gua osiriba isi mogh…®n gumaziba iniam.‚Äù  
\v 18 Aning an akam baraghav…®ra uan iveba ategha an g…®n zui.  
\v 19 Ez…® a mong s…®vagha ghuava, Sebedin otarim Jems uan dozim Jon ko aning…®n garima aning uan bot…®n ikiava uan iver ekiabar k…®ri.  
\v 20 An aning…®n garav…®ra aning…®n diaz…®ma, aning pura uan afeziam Sebedi koma an ingangarir gumaziba ataghiz…®ma me uan bot…®n itima aning Iesus…®n g…®n zui. 
\s1 Iesus duar kurar mam batoghez…®ma a gumazim ategha azenan ize 
\r (Luk 4:31-37) 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus ko an g…®n zuir darasi Kaperneam…®n ghue. Egha me zuima Sabat otoz…®ma, a God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven ghugha, d…®penir kam…®n aven itir gumazamiziba men sure gami.  
\v 22 A men sure gamima gumazamiziba bar an akam baregha d…®gavir kuram gami. An m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba mati gavgavim itir gumazim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba. An m…®g…®r…®g…®aba Judan arazibagh fozir gumazibar m…®g…®r…®g…®abar m…®n zuir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazamiziba d…®gavir kuram gami.\f + \ft (1:22) N…® Judan arazibagh fozir gumazibar m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f* 
\v 23 A kamagh…®n me m…®g…®av…®ra itima gumazir duar kuram apazazir mam izava God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven izegha dei.  
\v 24 A dia kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® manmagh…®n e damuasa, Nasaret…®n gumazim Iesus? N…® e gas…®ghas…®ghasa ize? K…® n…® g…®fo, n…® God amadazir gumazim, n…® God…®n damazim…®n zuezir gumazim.‚Äù  
\v 25 Ez…®ma Iesus akar gavgavim…®n kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® n…®m…®ra ik…®, egh gumazir kam ategh azenan izegh.‚Äù  
\v 26 Ez…® duar kurar kam Iesus bareghava gumazir kam gunabagha arav…®ram azenan ize.  
\v 27 Ez…® gumazamiziba bar bizir kam…®n ganigha guizbang…®ra d…®gavir kuram gamigha uarira uarir azangs…®si, ‚ÄúKar manmagh…®n amizir bizim? A suren arazir igiam e gami. A gavgavim itir akabav gei. A uaghan akar gavgavim…®n duar kurabav geima da an akam barasi.‚Äù  
\v 28 An amizir bizibar eghaghanim zuam…®ra Galilin Distrigh bar a garui. 
\s1 Iesus gumazamizir av…®ribar akuragha me gamima me ghuamaghe. 
\r (Matyu 8:14-17 ko Luk 4:38-41) 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus gumazir maba ko God ko m…®geir d…®penim ateghava Jems ko Jon sara, me Saimon ko Andrun d…®penim…®n ghue.  
\v 30 Me ghua garima Saimon…®n asamim ariava m…®karzim f…®ava dakozim gir…®ghav itima gumazir maba an gun Iesus m…®gei.  
\v 31 Me a m…®kemez…®ma, ez…® an a bagha ghuava an agharim…®n suiragha a ghufe. Ez…® an ar…®mariam anetaghiz…®ma a d…®kavigha dagheba me gan…®di. 
\p  
\v 32 Guarat…®zir kamra, am…®nim p…®riz…®ma me gumazamizir ar…®mariar kuraba koma duar kuraba apazaziba bar me inigha Iesus bagha izi.  
\v 33 Nguibar kam…®n itir gumazamiziba bar izava d…®penir kam…®n tiar akam…®n uari akufa.  
\v 34 Ez…®ma Iesus ar…®mariar guar av…®riba itir gumazamizir av…®riba men ar…®mariabagh amima me ghuamaghe. A duar kurar av…®riba sarama otoghez…®ma da gumazamiziba ategha azenan ize. Duar kuraba a g…®fo, a God…®n Otarim. Ez…® kamagh…®n a ghaze, ia kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…® suam, K…® God…®n Otarim. Egha a men anogoroke. 
\s1 Iesus gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganim…®n God ko m…®gei 
\r (Luk 4:42-44) 
\p  
\v 35 Egha am…®m…®zaraghan am…®nim t…®ghar itima, Iesus d…®kavigha d…®penim ategha ghuava gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganim…®n ghugha God ko m…®gei.  
\v 36 A ghuz…®ma Saimon uan roroaba ko a buriagharui.  
\v 37 Me ghuava an apighava kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazamiziba bar n…® buria gari.‚Äù  
\v 38 Ez…® Iesus men akam ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE nguibar igharazir rogh…®ra kagh itibar mangam. K…® uaghan munagh God…®n akam akunam. K…® bizir kam bagha ize.‚Äù  
\v 39 A kamagh…®n m…®kemegha, egha Galilin Distrigh…®n danganiba bar dagh aruava God ko m…®geir d…®penibar aven God…®n akam akurava gumazamizibagh apazazir duar kuraba batosi. 
\s1 Iesus lepa itir gumazir mam gamiz…®ma, a ua dera. 
\r (Matyu 8:1-4 ko Luk 5:12-16) 
\p  
\v 40 Ez…® gumazir lepa itir mam Iesus bagha izava, an guam…®n aviraghava tevimning ap…®righa puv…®ra a gaghori, ‚ÄúN…® fuegh…®va na damut…®, k…® God…®n damazim…®n zuegh ua deragham.‚Äù \f + \ft (1:40) Lepan ar…®mariar fom…®ra Baibel…®n dughiam…®n ikezim ighara. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n itir lepan ar…®mariam a igharaghav ami. Fom…®ra ikezim pura m…®karzir ghurghurim gumazir namnabar otifi. Egha uaghan bizir igharaziba sara posi.\f* 
\v 41 Iesus kamagh…®n oregha, guizbang…®ra bar an apangkufi. Egha uan agharim isa gumazir kam gat…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ifonge. N…®n m…®karzim zuegh, egh ua deragh.‚Äù  
\v 42 Iesus kamagh…®n m…®g…®av…®ra itima, lepan ar…®mariam zuam…®ra gumazir kam ataghiz…®ma an m…®karzim ua dera.  
\v 43 Ez…® Iesus gumazir kam amaga akar gavgavim…®n kamagh…®n a m…®gei,  
\v 44 ‚ÄúN…® oragh. N…® bizir kam…®n gun gumazir igharazitam m…®k…®man mark…®. N…® mang…® uan m…®karzim ofa gamir gumazim…®n akagh. Moses fom…®ra m…®kemezir arazim, n…® arazir kam…®n g…®n mang…®va, uan ar…®mariam g…®vazir bizim bagh God…®n ofa damu. N…® damight…®ma, me ganigh fogham, n…®n ar…®mariam guizbang…®ra g…®fa.‚Äù  
\v 45 Ez…®ma gumazir kam Iesus a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n damuan aghuaghava egha bizir kam bar me m…®gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma maburan av…®rim Iesus akuvaz…®ma, kamagh…®n a nguibar ekiatam…®n aven azenaram aruir puvat…®. A uab…®ra itir danganim…®n itima, gumazamiziba a bagha tintinibar izav…®ra iti. 
\c 2  
\s1 Iesus gumazir soroghafariba am…®razir mam gamiz…®ma a ua dera 
\r (Matyu 9:1-8 ko Luk 5:17-26) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® dughiar maba g…®vaz…®ma, Iesus uamategha Kaperneam…®n ghu. A ghuava d…®penim…®n itima gumazamizir av…®riba a uamatengezir akam baraki.  
\v 2 Me akar kam baregha izez…®ma d…®penim bar iz…®vaz…®ma an tiar akam sara iz…®fa. Ez…® Iesus God…®n akam me m…®k…®ri.  
\v 3 An akam akurima, gumazir maba gumazir soroghafariba aremezir mam inigha a bagha izi. Gumazir pumuning ko pumuning akuriam…®n a gisaghpugha izi.  
\v 4 Me iza garima d…®penim…®n tiar akam bar iz…®vaz…®ma, kamagh…®n me Iesus bagh mangan ibura. Egha me gumazir kam inigha d…®penir siriam…®n ghuavanabogha d…®penir siriam…®n torim gamigha beniba akuriam dafegha anemadaz…®ma a Iesus bagha ghuaghiri.\f + \ft (2:4) Judabar d…®peniba boksiabar m…®n gari. Dar inogoriba puvat…®gha, egha p…®n barafi. Ez…® dar m…®riabar azenan adidiaba iti. Dar d…®penir ak…®niba puvat…®. Me pura nguazim gis…®n dar ingari.\f* 
\v 5 Ez…® Iesus gumazir kabar n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n ganigha kamagh…®n soroghafariba am…®razir gumazim m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan borim, n…®n arazir kuraba g…®fa.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®geima, Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba apiaghav ikiava uarira uan navir averiabar kamagh m…®gei,  
\v 7 ‚ÄúGumazir kam tizim bagha kamagh…®n m…®gei? A God…®n danganim iniasava ami! Gumazir k…®nitam gumazir igharazitam…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amadaghan kogham. God uab…®ra.‚Äù  
\v 8 Me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zima, Iesus zuam…®ra uan navir averiam…®n men n…®ghn…®zibagh fogha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa manmagh sua kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si?  
\v 9 K…® akar manam m…®k…®mam? Pura gumazir k…®nitam kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, k…® n…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amada. Egh uaghan gumazir k…®nitam kamagh…®n m…®k…®man kogham, n…® d…®kavigh uan akuriam inigh mang…®, egh ua deragh.  
\v 10 K…® arazir kam damight…®ma, ia ganigh fogham, Gumazibar Otarim a nguazir kam…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amangamin gavgavim iti.‚Äù Egha a kamagh…®n gumazir soroghafariba am…®razim m…®gei,  
\v 11 ‚ÄúK…® n…® m…®gei, n…® d…®kavigh uan akuriam inigh d…®penim…®n mang…®.‚Äù  
\v 12 Egha a m…®g…®av…®ra itima me garima gumazir kam d…®kavighava uan akuriam inigha azenan ghu. Gumazamiziba bar an ganigha d…®gavir kuram gamigha God…®n ziam fava kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE faragha bizir katam…®n ganizir puvat…®!‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus uab…®n g…®n mangasa Livain dei 
\r (Matyu 9:9-13 ko Luk 5:27-32) 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Iesus ua Galilin d…®par m…®riam…®n ghuaghiri. A ghuaghirima, gumazamizir av…®riba izava uari akuvaz…®ma, a men sure gami.  
\v 14 A men sure gamuava d…®par m…®riam…®n ghuava Alfius…®n otarim Livain garima, a gavman dan…®ngamin dag…®aba isir d…®penim…®n aperaghav iti. Iesus an garava, kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan g…®n iz…®.‚Äù Ez…® Livai a baregha, d…®kavigha an g…®n zui.\f + \ft (2:14) Matyun ziar igharazim kara, Livai.\f* 
\p  
\v 15 Egha g…®n Iesus Livain d…®penim…®n ikiava uan suren gumaziba koma api. Dag…®aba isir gumazir av…®riba koma arazir kurabagh amir gumazir av…®riba, me uaghan me koma api. Gumazir kamagh…®n amir av…®riba, me uaghan Iesus…®n g…®n arui.  
\v 16 Ez…® me apa itima, Judan arazibagh fozir Farisin gumaziba me an ganigha, egha an suren gumazibar azangs…®si, ‚ÄúA manmagh sua dag…®aba isir gumaziba ko arazir kurabagh amir gumaziba koma api?‚Äù\f + \ft (2:16) Farisibar arazir av…®riba iti. Gumazamizir men arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®ziba me kamagh…®n g…®n…®ghn…®si, me God…®n damazim…®n derazir puvat…®. Farisiba kamagh…®n dag…®aba isir gumazibagh n…®ghn…®si, me Rom…®n gavman bagha dag…®aba isi. Kamagh…®n amiz…® me uaghan God…®n damazim…®n derazir puvat…®. Me kamagh…®n amuava Rom…®n gumaziba ko arazir kurabagh ami.\f* 
\v 17 Ez…® Iesus men azangs…®zim baregha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúAr…®mariaba puvat…®zir gumaziba, dokta bagha zuir puvat…®. Gumazir ar…®mariaba itibara, me dokta bagha zui. K…® God…®n damazim…®n derazir gumaziba bagha izezir puvat…®. K…® gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amibar d…®masa ize!‚Äù 
\s1 Me God ko m…®k…®masa dagheba atagharazir arazim bagha Iesus…®n azangs…®si 
\r (Matyu 9:14-17 ko Luk 5:33-39) 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® dughiar mam Jon…®n suren gumaziba koma Farisin suren gumaziba me God ko m…®k…®masa dagheba ataghrasi. Ez…® Iesus…®n suren gumaziba dughiar kam…®n apima gumazir maba Iesus bagha izava kamagh…®n an azangs…®si, ‚ÄúKar manmagh…®n amizir arazim? Jon…®n suren gumaziba koma Farisin suren gumaziba me dat…®r…®gh…®n God ko m…®k…®masa dagheba ataghrazima, n…®n suren gumaziba God ko m…®k…®masa dagheba ataghrazir puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 19 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúGumazitam amuim…®n ikiasa isar ekiam gamuava gumazir mabar diaz…®ma me ize. A me ko ik…®t…®ma, me manmagh…®n damuam, me dagheba ategham, o? puvat…®gham. A me ko ik…®t…®ma me dagheba ataghraghan kogham.  
\v 20 Me dagheba ataghrazir dughiam iti. Dughiar kam iz…®t…®ma, gumazitaba amuim…®n ikiamin gumazim…®n suiragh mang…®t…® me dughiar kam dagheba ataghragham. 
\p  
\v 21 ‚ÄúEgh gumazitam inir av…®zir igiatam inigha korotiar ghuritam porogha a isamizir puvat…®. A kamagh…®n damigh…®va egh a rut…®ma inir av…®zir igiam ekonegh korotiar ghurim gekuigh, anebight…®ma an torim guizbang…®ra bar ekevegham.  
\v 22 Eght…® gumazitam wain…®n igiam inigh…®va, as…®zir inir m…®sevir ghurim…®n a ruighan kogham. A kamagh…®n damight…®ma wain buva as…®zir inir m…®sevir ghurim bigh…®va, wain ko as…®zir inim, aning v…®rara ikuvigham. A kamagh…®n damuan kogham. A wain…®n igiam inigh as…®zir inir m…®sevir igiamra ruigham.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus Sabat…®n Ekiam 
\r (Matyu 12:1-8 ko Luk 6:1-5) 
\p  
\v 23 Egha Iesus Sabat…®n dughiar mam…®n, raiz…®n m…®n garir dagher mam, wit, me an azenir ekiam…®n torim…®n zui. An suren gumaziba a ko ghuava wit…®n ov…®ziba kuara zui.\f + \ft (2:23) N…® wit…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f* 
\v 24 Me zuima Farisin maba men ganigha kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® gan. Me manmagh sua arazir kam gamuava Sabat…®n arazim…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® Iesus me ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa, Devit amizir bizim me an osiriz…®ma a iti, ia an ganizir puvat…®? A uan gumaziba ko me m…®tiriam men azima a bizir kam gami.  
\v 26 A ghuava God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ghugha God gan…®ngizir bretba ame. A da apava, uaghan maba isa uan gumazibagh an…®ngiz…®ma, me uaghan ame. Dughiar kam Abiatar, ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim itima, Devit dame. Judabar arazir kam iti. Bret…®n kaba ofa gamir gumazibara dapi, gumazir k…®niba puvat…®. Ez…® Devit, gumazir k…®nim, bret…®n kaba ame.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 27 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod gumazibar akurvaghasa Sabat at…®. A Sabat bagha gumaziba at…®zir puvat…®.  
\v 28 Ez…® Gumazibar Otarim a Sabat…®n dughiam…®n Ekiam.‚Äù\f + \ft (2:28) N…® Gumazibar Otarim…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f* 
\c 3  
\s1 Iesus Sabat…®n dafarim ekonezir gumazir mam gamiz…®ma a ua dera 
\r (Matyu 12:9-14 ko Luk 6:6-11) 
\p  
\v 1-2 Egha dughiar igharazir mam Iesus God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n ghuava, garima dafarim ekonezir gumazir mam gumazamizir av…®ribar tong…®n d…®penir kam…®n aven iti. A itima gumazir maba uaghan iti. Me, Iesus bizitam damight…®ma, me akam agasasa bar derav…®ra an gari. Me kamagh sua an gari. A Sabat…®n gumazir kam…®n akuragham, o?  
\v 3 Me bizir kam bagha an garav…®ra itima, Iesus kamagh…®n dafarim ekonezir gumazim m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh iz…® bar en guam…®n tugh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Gumazim d…®kavigha tuz…®ma, Iesus kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúArazir manam Sabat…®n arazim ab…®ki? E arazir aghuim damuam, o arazir kuram damuam, o gumazim…®n akuragham, o gumazim gas…®ghas…®gham?‚Äù A kamagh…®n men azaraz…®ma, me bar n…®m…®ra iti. 
\p  
\v 5 An damazimning bar gumazamizibagh aruava, navim…®n aven men atari. A men garima, men naviba gavgavigha apangkuvir n…®ghn…®ziba men puvat…®. Kamagh…®n a bar osemegha gumazim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan dafarim onegh.‚Äù Ez…® gumazir kam uan dafarim onez…®ma, an dafarim ua dera.  
\v 6 Ez…® Farisiba ikia ganigha d…®penim ategha azenan izegha Herot…®n gumaziba ko ikia Iesus…®n m…®soghasa akabar k…®ri. 
\ms1 Iesus uan gavgavim men akaz…®ma an adarasi n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®. 
\mr (Sapta 3:7-6:6) 
\s1 Gumazamizir av…®riba Iesus…®n g…®n zui 
\r (Luk 6:17-19) 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Iesus uan suren gumaziba koma Galilin d…®pam…®n ghuaghiri. A ghuaghirima gumazamizir av…®riba Galilin Distrigh…®n ikegha an g…®n ghuaghiri.  
\v 8 Gumazamizir av…®riba Judian Distrigh koma Jerusalem…®n nguibam koma Idumean Distrigh ko Jordan…®n d…®pam…®n vong…®n itir danganiba koma Tair ko Saidon…®n nguibamning ikegha, me Iesus bagha ghuaghiri. Gumazamizir av…®rir kaba, me an amizir bizibar akam bareghava a bagha ghuaghiri.  
\v 9-10 Me iraghuez…®ma, Iesus gumazamizir av…®riba men akuraz…®ma, men ar…®mariaba g…®fa. Ar…®mariaba itir gumazamizir av…®riba uan ar…®mariaba g…®vasa Iesus…®n borogh…®n uari akuvagha, Iesus…®n suighasa uari munamadi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, Iesus uan suren gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa bot…®n tam inigh iz…® puram anet…®ght…® a ik…®. Eght…® gumazamiziba bar na akuvaght…®ma k…® bot…®n ghuavanangam.‚Äù  
\v 11 Iesus me m…®geima, duar kuraba apazazir gumazir maba izava, Iesus…®n garava duar kuraba zuam…®ra me gamima me Iesus…®n guam…®n daigh…®ra kamagh…®n arai, ‚ÄúN…® God…®n Otarim.‚Äù  
\v 12 Me kamagh…®n amima, an akar gavgavim…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…®, ‚ÄòN…® God…®n Otarim.‚Äô‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus 12 plan aposelba me am…®sefe 
\r (Matyu 10:1-4 ko Luk 6:12-16) 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Iesus d…®par m…®riam…®n ikegha d…®kavighava m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuavanabogha uan ifongezir gumazibar diaz…®ma, me a bagha zui.  
\v 14 Me zuima a gumazir 12 pla m…®sevegha ziar kam, aposelba, me gat…®. Eght…® me a ko ik…®t…®, a g…®n me amadaght…® me mang…® God…®n akar aghuim akunam.  
\v 15 Egh a uan gavgavim me dan…®ngt…®ma me uaghan duar kuraba batogham.  
\v 16 A m…®sevezir gumazir 12 plan ziabar kara. Saimon (Iesus g…®n ziar kam, Pita, a gat…®),  
\v 17 Sebedin otarimning Jems ko Jon (A ziar kam aning gat…®, Boanerges. Ziar kam…®n m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu, atara pamtem m…®geir gumazimning),  
\v 18 Andru ko Filip, Bartolomyu, Matyu, Tomas, Alfius…®n otarim Jems, Tadius, Saimon (a Selotiabar gumazir mam),  
\v 19 ko Judas Iskariot, gumazir Iesus isava, apanibagh an…®ngizim. 
\s1 Me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIesus Belsebul…®n gavgavim…®n ingari‚Äù 
\r (Matyu 12:24-32 ko Luk 11:14-23 ko 12:10) 
\p  
\v 20 Egha Iesus uamategha d…®penim…®n aven ghugha itima gumazamizir av…®riba izava anekufa. Me bar anekuvaz…®ma kamagh…®n a uan suren gumaziba koma me daghebar aman ibura. Me damamin dughiaba puvat…®.  
\v 21 Ez…® gumazamizir maba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAn ongani.‚Äù Ez…® Iesus…®n adarasi akar kam bareghava, a inigh mangasa izi. 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® Judan arazibagh fozir gumazir maba Jerusalem…®n ikegha izaghrava kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúBelsebul a gapasa. A duar kurabar gumazir dapanim…®n gavgavim…®n duar kuraba batosi.‚Äù\f + \ft (3:22) Satan…®n ziar mamra kara, Belsebul.\f* 
\p  
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus me m…®geir akam bareghava, egha kamagh…®n gumazamizibar diaghava akar is…®n zuir maba me m…®gei, ‚ÄúSatan manmagh…®n uab…®ra uab…® batuegham?  
\v 24 Kantrin tam tong…®ra uari ab…®gh…®va uarira uariv sogh…®va kantrin kam ikian kogham.  
\v 25 Kamagh…®n uaghan, d…®penir vam…®ran itir darasi me tong…®ra uari ab…®gh…®va uarira uariv sogh d…®penir kam…®n itir darasi ikian kogham.  
\v 26 Kamagh…®ra Satan…®n adarazi uarira uari ab…®gh…®va uariv m…®soght…®ma an gavgavim bar g…®vagh…®va ikian kogham. 
\p  
\v 27 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazir manam puram aven mang…® gumazir gavgavitam…®n d…®penim akarigh…®va an biziba okemegham? Puvat…®gham. A faraghv…®ra benibar gumazir gavgavir kam ikegham. A kamagh…®n a damigh gumazir kam…®n d…®penim…®n aven mang…®, an biziba okemegham. 
\p  
\v 28 ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, gumazamizibar arazir kuraba ko me God…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®zir akaba, God da g…®n amangamin tuavim iti.  
\v 29 Eght…® gumazitam God…®n Duam…®n ziam gas…®ghasight…®ma God an arazir kurar kam, a g…®n amadaghan kogham. Egh gumazir kam aremeght…®, arazir kurar kam an ik…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù  
\v 30 Me faragha kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúDuar kurar mam a gapasa.‚Äù A bizir kam bagha, akar kabar me m…®gei.\f + \ft (3:30) Iesus God…®n Duam…®n gavgavim…®n ingari. Ez…® me ghaze, a Satan…®n gavgavim…®n ingari. Me kamagh…®n God…®n Duam…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®si.\f* 
\s1 Iesus…®n amebam ko an doziba 
\r (Matyu 12:46-50 ko Luk 8:19-21) 
\p  
\v 31 Ez…®ma Iesus…®n amebam ko doziba izava, a itir d…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n tughava gumazir mam amadaz…®ma a Iesus…®n m…®k…®masa aven zui.  
\v 32 Gumazamizir av…®riba a koma apiaghav ikiava kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh, n…®n amebam ko doziba me n…® bagha izeghava azenan iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 33 Me a m…®kemez…®ma a kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúTina nan amebam? Te nan doziba?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 34 A kamagh…®n men azaraghava, an okarigha apiaghav itir gumazamizibar garava, kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gan! Nan amebam ko dozibara kara.  
\v 35 Gumazamizir God ifongezir arazibar g…®n zuiba, me nan doziba ko nan amiziba ko nan amebam.‚Äù 
\c 4  
\s1 Iesus akar is…®n zuim…®n kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir mam wit…®n ov…®ziba inigha azenim…®n da kuragharui‚Äù 
\r (Matyu 13:1-23 ko Luk 8:4-15) 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar igharazir mam Iesus ua d…®par m…®riam…®n ikiava, gumazamizir mabar sure gami. Me an akaba baraghasa anekuvagha guizbang…®ra bar av…®raseme. Ez…® a bot…®n mam…®n b…®ragha d…®pam gis…®n aperaghav iti. Gumazamizir kaba an borogh…®n dadarim…®n apiaghav iti.  
\v 2 An akar is…®n zuir av…®ribar men sure gamuava, kamagh…®n me m…®gei,  
\v 3 ‚ÄúIa oragh. Gumazir mam raiz…®n m…®ngarir daghem, wit, a inigha ghua uan azenim…®n da akuragharui.  
\v 4 A da akurima wit…®n ov…®zir maba tuavim…®n irez…®ma, kuaraziba iza da ame.  
\v 5 Ez…® maba dag…®abagh is…®n itir nguazir evarim gire. Nguazir kam m…®temezir puvat…®, ez…®ma wit…®n ov…®ziba zuam…®ra afuangi.  
\v 6 Ez…® dar biba bar nguazim…®n aven iraghuezir puvat…®, ez…® aruem anaga dagh isiraz…®, ez…® da isia m…®s…®ngi.  
\v 7 Ez…® wit…®n ov…®zir maba benir d…®koniba itir nguazim giregha, benibar tong…®n afuangiz…®, benir d…®koniba aghuava beniba da ikiaghar…®ki. Ez…® dar ov…®ziba m…®sevezir puvat…®.  
\v 8 Ez…® wit…®n ov…®zir maba nguazir aghuim giregha aghuava dagheba m…®sefi. Egha maba 30 pla m…®sevima maba 60 pla m…®sefe. Ez…® maba ghua 100…®n tu.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Iesus me m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúTina kuarimning iti, an oragh.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus manmagh suav…®ra akar is…®n zuibagh ami 
\p  
\v 10 Gumazamizir av…®riba bar ghuez…®, ez…® Iesus uab…®ra itima, an 12 plan gumaziba koma an borogh…®n itir gumaziba, me an akar is…®n zuim…®n m…®ngarim bagha an azara.  
\v 11 Me an azaraz…®ma a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod fofozim ia gan…®ngiz…®ma, ia God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akar mogomeba dagh fo. Egha k…® azenan itir gumazamiziba pura akar is…®n zuibar me m…®gei.  
\v 12 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄòMe zurazurara gan…®va, me bizitam g…®foghan kogham. 
\q2 Me uaghan zurazurara oragh…®va, 
\q3 me deraghv…®ra akar m…®ngaritam g…®foghan kogham. 
\q1 Me amuava akar m…®ngarim g…®fogha, uan navibagh iraz…®, 
\q2 God men arazir kuraba g…®n amadaghai.‚Äô‚Äù\f + \ft (4:12) Iesus God…®n g…®n mangasa gumazamizibar anogorozir puvat…®. Marazi uari God…®n g…®n mangan aghua.\f* 
\s1 Wit…®n akar is…®n zuim…®n m…®ngarim 
\p  
\v 13 An akar kam me m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa wit…®n akar is…®n zuir kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®fozir puvat…®? Ia manmagh…®n akar is…®n zuir igharazir tabagh fogham?  
\v 14 Akar is…®n zuim…®n aven itir gumazir kam a mati gumazir God…®n akam kuragharuim  
\v 15 Gumazir maba tuavim girezir wit…®n ov…®zibar m…®n ami. Me God…®n akaba baraghiz…® Satan zuam…®ra izava me oraghizir God…®n akaba, me dama ada ini.  
\v 16 Gumazir maba dag…®aba itir nguazim girezir wit…®n ov…®zibar m…®n ami. Me God…®n akaba bareghava da bagha bar akonge.  
\v 17 Egha men biba iraghuezir puvat…®gha, egha uaghan dughiar ruarim…®n itir puvat…®. Me itima os…®mt…®ziba ko God…®n g…®n zuir gumazibagh as…®ghas…®zir araziba izima, me pura God ataki.  
\v 18 Gumazir maba benir d…®koniba itir nguazim girezir wit…®n ov…®zibar m…®n ami. Me God…®n akaba baraki.  
\v 19 Me da bareghava me uaghan nguazir kam…®n os…®mt…®ziba bagha n…®ghn…®ghava, dag…®ar av…®riba iniasa ifavarir n…®ghn…®zibagh amuava, nguazir kam…®n bizir av…®ribar garava da bagha agoi. Bizir kabar n…®ghn…®ziba izava God…®n akaba ikiaghar…®z…®ma da m…®sevir puvat…®.  
\v 20 Ez…® gumazir maba nguazir aghuim girezir wit…®n ov…®zibar m…®n ami. Me God…®n akaba baregha dar suiragha dar g…®n zui. Egha me m…®sefi. Maba 30 pla m…®sevima, maba 60 pla m…®sefi. Ez…® maba ghua 100…®n tu.‚Äù 
\s1 Lam…®n danganimra aneguragh 
\r (Luk 8:16-18) 
\p  
\v 21 Egha Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIan tina lam gaboroghava a inigha itarir ekiam…®n anevara? O an a inigha dakozim…®n apengan anet…®? Puvat…®! Ia a daborogh a inigh azenan an danganimra aneguragh.  
\v 22 Kamagh…®ra mogomer biziba da g…®n azenan otivigham. Eght…® bizir amigha aveziba da uaghan g…®n azenan otivigham.  
\v 23 Tina kuarimning iti, an oragh.‚Äù \f + \ft (4:23) Iesus akar is…®n zuibar gumazamizibar sure gami. A kamagh…®n foghasa, me guizbang…®ra God gifongez ti puvat…®. Gumazir God gifongeziba, akar is…®n zuiba baregha, dagh n…®ghn…®ghava g…®n dar m…®ngaribar gara dagh fo. Ez…® gumazir God gifongezir puvat…®ziba, n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, akar is…®n zuiba, eghaghanir onganiba. Kamagh…®n me akar is…®n zuiba, dagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®gha, dar m…®ngaribar garir puvat…®.\f* 
\p  
\v 24-25 Egha a m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa deraghv…®ra akar kam baragh. Ia deraghv…®ra a baragh…®va deragh fogh, eght…® God uan akabar fofozir av…®riba ia dan…®ngam. God…®n akabagh fozir gumazitam a God…®n akar igharaziba uaghan da baragham. Eght…® God…®n akabagh foghan aghuazir gumazitam, an fofozir muziarim God a dama inigham. Ia God…®n akam barazi mogh…®n God uaghan kamagh…®n damuva, bizir av…®rir maba sara ia damuam.‚Äù 
\s1 Dagher ov…®zir afuarazibar akar is…®n zuim 
\p  
\v 26 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n arazim kamak…®n. Gumazir mam dagher ov…®ziba inigha nguazim…®n da kuri.  
\v 27 Gumazir kam da kunighava, d…®magaribar akuava, aruebar d…®kavigha arui. An aruima dagher ov…®zir kaba da afuegha aghui. Dagher ov…®zir kaba manmagh…®n afuegha aghui? Gumazir kam fozir puvat…®.  
\v 28 Ez…® nguazimra dagher ov…®zir kabagh amiz…®ma da aghua m…®sefe. Da faragha afuegha aghua ghua aghariba otivigha egha adava ghua ak…®mariba otivigha m…®sefe.  
\v 29 Da m…®sevegha dagheba itima, gumazir kam sabam inighava dar akori. A fo, dagheba iti, ez…® dar akoramin dughiam oto.‚Äù 
\s1 Mastet…®n ov…®zim…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Matyu 13:31-32 ko Luk 13:18-19) 
\p  
\v 30 Egha a ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE manmagh…®n God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n arazim m…®k…®mam? O, e akar is…®n zuir manam…®n an m…®ngarim…®n gun m…®k…®mam?  
\v 31 A mastet…®n ov…®zim…®n m…®n gari. Mastet…®n zuravarir ov…®ziba bar sufi. Temer igharazibar ov…®ziba bar a gafiragha ekefe.\f + \ft (4:31) N…® mastet…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f* 
\v 32 Gumazir mam anekuniz…®ma a g…®n aghua bar ekeveghava azenim…®n itir zuravariba bar dagh afiragha bar ekefe. An ekevegha an aguar ekiaba uari tuiraz…®ma kuaraziba izava an aguabar dughuazim…®n aven ikia m…®konibar ingari.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 33 Egha Iesus men n…®ghn…®ziba tuz…®naghara m…®n amir akar is…®n zuir av…®ribar God…®n akabar me m…®gei.  
\v 34 An akabar gumazamizibav g…®ava zurara akar is…®n zuibar me m…®gei. Egha a uan suren gumaziba ko me uarira ikiava a bizibar m…®ngariba ab…®gha me m…®gei. 
\s1 Iesus am…®nir ekiam ko d…®pavs…®zim batoghez…®ma aning pura n…®m…®ra ir…®ghav iti 
\r (Matyu 8:23-27 ko Luk 8:22-25) 
\p  
\v 35 Aruer kam…®n am…®nim p…®rasava amima Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúE d…®par kam atugh an vong…®n mangam.‚Äù  
\v 36 A kamagh…®n me m…®geima gumazamiziba dadarim…®n ikiav…®ra iti. Ez…® me Iesus aperaghav itir bot…®n ghuavanabogha pul gamua vong…®n zui. Bot…®n igharazir maba uaghan me ko vong…®n zui.  
\v 37 Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko zuima, Maia! Am…®nir ekiam d…®kafi. Ez…® d…®pavs…®ziba izava bot gafiraz…® d…®pam bot…®n aven ghuaghira, bot giz…®fa, ez…® an atam d…®pam…®n aven mag…®rasava ami.  
\v 38 Bot mag…®rasava amima, Iesus bot…®n kam…®n g…®rak…®rang…®n dapanir aghoghonir mam uan dapanim…®n aghorogha akui. Ez…® an suren gumaziba a gaghuragha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, e g…®fa! N…® e bagha n…®ghn…®si, o puvat…®?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 39 Ez…® Iesus d…®kavigha tugha am…®nim batogha, egha d…®pavs…®zim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua am…®ragh, egh n…®m…®ra ik…®!‚Äù A m…®geima, am…®nim am…®raz…®ma, d…®pam pura n…®m…®ra ir…®ghav iti. 
\p  
\v 40 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha puv atiati? Ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim otevegha kamagh…®ra iti?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 41 Ez…® me bar atiatigha kamagh…®n uarira uariv gei, ‚ÄúGumazir kam tinara? Am…®nim ko d…®pavs…®zim uaghan an akam barasi!‚Äù 
\c 5  
\s1 Iesus Gerasan gumazir mam…®n duar kuraba batoghez…®ma da anetaki 
\r (Matyu 8:28-34 ko Luk 8:26-39) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus uan suren gumaziba koma d…®pam atugha vong…®n Gerasan danganim…®n oto.  
\v 2 Me otivigha, Iesus bot ategha dadarim…®n anadima gumazir duar kuram apazazir mam, a matmatiam…®n ikegha Iesus bativasa izi.  
\v 3-4 A matmatiam…®n ikiava a gakui. Me dughiar av…®riba senbar an agharimning ikiava, ankavba an suemning gazui. Ez…® a zurara sen…®n kabar suighava dar aghora egha an suemning ikezir ankavbav sogha dar aghoraghar…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma gumazitam gumazir kam…®n suiragh a ik…®va avegham. Me uaghan senbar a ikeght…® da an suiraghan kogham. Egh gumazitam gavgavigh a ikeghan kogham.  
\v 5 A d…®magariba ko aruebar matmatiam ko m…®ghs…®abar purama aruava pamtem arava dag…®abar uab…® uan m…®karzim aghori. 
\p  
\v 6 A saghon ikia Iesus…®n ganigha ivegha a bagha izava an guam…®n uan tevimning ap…®ri.  
\v 7-8 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n duar kuram m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® duar kuram, n…® gumazir kam ategh azenan iz…®.‚Äù Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®geima, ez…® gumazir kam pamtem arava kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® manmagh…®n na damuasa, Iesus biziba bar dar p…®n itir God…®n Otarim. K…® God…®n damazim…®n pamtem n…®n azangs…®si, n…® na gas…®ghas…®ghan mark…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 A kamagh…®n m…®geima Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan ziam d…®borogh.‚Äù Ez…® duar kurar kam a ikaragha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE bar av…®raseme, kamagh…®n nan ziam Av…®riba.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 A Iesus danganir igharazitam me amangan aghuagha Iesus v…®v…®gha a gakaghori. 
\p  
\v 11 Dughiar kam, men borogh…®ra itir m…®ghs…®ar m…®riam…®n dar av…®riba ikiava api.  
\v 12 Ez…® duar kurar kaba kamagh…®n Iesus m…®g…®ava a gakaghori, ‚ÄúN…® e m…®kemegh e amadaght…®ma e mang…®va dar b…®zir munabagh apazaka.‚Äù  
\v 13 Ez…® a men amamangat…®z…®ma duar kurar kaba gumazir kam ategha azenan izegha ghua dar b…®zim gapasa. Dar av…®rir kaba, dar d…®bobonim 2,000…®n borogh…®n ghu. Ez…® daba puv ivemara ghuaghira davarir kuram giraghueghava d…®pam…®n aven ghuegha d…®pam apava ariagh…®re. 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® dabar garir gumaziba daba batoghezir bizim…®n ganigha ghua nguibar ekiam…®n ghua danganir kam…®n itir nguibar dozibar ghua bizir otozir kam…®n gun m…®gei. Gumazamiziba bizir kam…®n ganasa d…®kavigha izi.  
\v 15 Me izava Iesus borogh…®n duar kuraba apazazir gumazim…®n garima, an n…®ghn…®zim ua deraz…®ma, a uan korotiaba aghuighava aperaghav iti. Me an ganighava atiatingi.  
\v 16 Ez…® otozir bizir kam…®n ganizir gumazamiziba, me duar kuraba apazazir gumazim…®n bizir otozir kabar gumazir igharazibav gei. Me dar gun m…®g…®ava ghuava uaghan daba batozir bizim…®n gun m…®gei.  
\v 17 Gumazamizir kaba bizir kam bareghava uan danganim ategh mangasa kamagh…®n me Iesus m…®g…®a a gaghori. 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® Iesus danganir kam ategh mangasa bot…®n b…®rima duar kuraba apazazir gumazim Iesus ko mangasa pamtem a gaghori.  
\v 19 Ez…® Iesus an anogoregha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uamategh uan adarazi bagh d…®penim…®n mang…®va Gumazir Ekiam n…®n akuragha n…® gamizir bizibar gun me m…®k…®m…®va egh a uaghan bar n…®n apangkuvizir bizim…®n gun me m…®k…®m.‚Äù  
\v 20 Gumazir kam a bareghava ghua Iesus an akurazir bizim…®n gun Dekapolis…®n Distrigh…®n itir nguibabar ghua bar me m…®gei. Gumazamizir kaba a bareghava d…®gavir kuram gami. 
\s1 Iesus aremezir guivir mam koma ar…®mariar amizir mam gamiz…®ma aning ua dera 
\r (Matyu 9:18-26 ko Luk 8:40-56) 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus bot inigha uamategha d…®pam…®n vong…®n ize. A izegha d…®par dadarim…®n itima gumazamizir av…®riba izava anekufa.  
\v 22-23 Ez…® God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n bizibar garir gumazir mam, an ziam Jairus, a izava, Iesus…®n garava an guam…®n uab…® ekunigha kamagh…®n puv…®ram a gaghori, ‚ÄúNan guivim aremeghasa an d…®ghorimra isi. N…® iz…®va uan dafarim a dat…®ght…® an ar…®mariam g…®vagh ua ikiam.‚Äù  
\v 24 Ez…® kamagh…®n Iesus a ko zui. 
\p A zuima gumazamizir av…®riba bar anekuvaghava an g…®n zui.  
\v 25 Me zuima men tong…®n ghuzim batir ar…®mariar amizir mam uaghan me ko zui. Amizir kam, ghuzim batir ar…®mariam an itima 12 plan azeniba g…®fa.  
\v 26 A fom…®ra ar…®mariam a g…®vasava doktaba bagha zuima, me an ar…®mariam a g…®vazir puvat…®. Ez…® a m…®zazir kuram isi. A uan ar…®mariam a g…®vasava pura uan dag…®abar me g…®vezima an dag…®aba bar g…®fa. Bizir kaba an ar…®mariam…®n akurazir puvat…®. An ek…®va ghuav…®ra iti.  
\v 27-28 A Iesus amir bizibar akam baregha, a kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúK…® puram an azenan itir korotiamra suiragh nan ar…®mariam g…®vagham.‚Äù A kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghava egha damuasa. A gumazamizir av…®ribar g…®n izava me munamaga izava Iesus…®n korotiam…®n suira.  
\v 29 Amizim an korotiam…®n suighav…®ra, an ghuzir ar…®mariam pura dutugha ghu. A uab…® uab…® baregha fo, an m…®karzim ua dera. 
\p  
\v 30 A kamagh…®n amimra, Iesus zuam…®ra uab…® uab…® baregha a God gumazibar ar…®mariaba g…®vaghasa a gan…®ngizir gavgavim, an m…®karzim ataghiz…® a fo, nan gavgavim ingari. Egha a ragha gumazamizibar garava men azara, ‚ÄúTina nan korotiam…®n suira?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 31 Ez…® an suren gumaziba a ikaragha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® garima, gumazamizir av…®riba n…® akufa. Ez…® n…® tizim bagha kamagh…®n azai, ‚ÄòTina nan korotiam…®n suira?‚Äô‚Äù 
\p  
\v 32 Me kamagh…®n Iesus m…®g…®av…®ra itima Iesus uan korotiam…®n suirazir gumazim g…®foghasa raghr…®gha garagharui.  
\v 33 A ruiav…®ra itima, amizir kam a batozir bizim g…®fogha izava Iesus…®n guam…®n degiaghr…®gha, atiatia n…®ghava guizbang…®ra a batozir bizim…®n gun a m…®gei.  
\v 34 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan guivim, n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan iti. Ez…® n…®n ar…®mariam g…®fa. N…® navir am…®r…®zim…®n mang…®, eght…® n…®n ar…®mariar kam ua n…® damuan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 35 Iesus amizir kam m…®g…®av…®ra itima gumazir maba God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n bizibar garir gumazim, Jairus…®n d…®penim…®n ikeghava ize. Me izegha kamagh…®n Jairus m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n guivim areme. N…® os…®mt…®zim Tisa dan…®ngan mark…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 36 Me kamagh…®n m…®geima Iesus me baregha kamagh…®n Jairus m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® atiatingan mark…®. N…® pura n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ik…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 37 An g…®n aruir gumaziba a ko mangasa amima a men anogoregha, egha Pita, ko Jon an dozim Jems, merara inigha me zui.  
\v 38 Me ghua Jairus…®n d…®penim…®n otivigha Iesus gumazamiziba barazima, me bar azia n…®g…®nir dafam gami. 
\p  
\v 39 A me bagha aven ghua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha azia n…®g…®nir dafam gami? Borir kam aremezir puvat…®. An akui.‚Äù  
\v 40 A kamagh…®n me m…®geima, me a d…®povava an ingarava kava uariv gei, ‚ÄúE fo, a guizbang…®ram areme.‚Äù Gumazamiziba kamagh…®n m…®geima ez…® a bar me batuegha guivim…®n afeziam ko amebam inigha an suren gumazir pumuning ko m…®kezim, merara a ko zui. A me inigha me guivim…®n kuam itir danganim…®n aven zui.  
\v 41 Me ghuegha a guivim…®n agharim suiragha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúTalita kum!‚Äù (Akar kam…®n m…®ngarim kamagh…®n iti, ‚ÄúGuivir dozim, k…® n…® m…®gei, n…® d…®kafigh!‚Äù)  
\v 42 An a m…®geimrama, guivim d…®kavigha tughava arui. (An azenir 12 pla.) A d…®kavigha tugha aruima, me kamagh…®n guizbang…®ra d…®gavir kuram gami.  
\v 43 Ez…® an akar gavgavim…®n guizbang…®ra me m…®g…®a ghaze, ia bizir kam…®n gun gumazir igharazitam m…®k…®mam mark…®. A kamagh…®n me m…®g…®ava daghetam a dan…®ngasa me m…®gei. 
\c 6  
\s1 Iesus…®n nguibam…®n itir darasi an aghuagha ak…®rim a gasara 
\r (Matyu 13:53-58 ko Luk 4:16-30) 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Iesus kagh tegha uan nguibam…®n ghuavanadima an suren gumaziba a ko zui.  
\v 2 Ez…®, Sabat…®n dughiam otoz…®ma a God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven ghua, gumazamizibar sure gami. Gumazamizir av…®riba an akaba bareghava d…®gavir kuram gami. 
\p Me d…®gavir kuram gamigha azara, ‚ÄúGumazir kam managh akar kaba ini? A managh n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ini? A uaghan managh mirakelbagh amir gavgavim ini?  
\v 3 E fo, kar pura d…®penibar ingarir gumazim. A Marian otarim, a Jems ko Josep, Judas, Saimon, a men avebamra. An buaramiziba e ko iti.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma me d…®bovir akabar a m…®g…®ava navibar aven an atari. 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, a nguibar igharazibar zuima, me an ziam fe. Ez…® an nguibam…®n an adarasi, me an ziam fer puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 5 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma a nguibar kam…®n mirakel…®n av…®ribagh amizir puvat…®. A pura dafarim ar…®mariar gumazir vabara me gar…®ghiz…®ma, men ar…®mariaba g…®fa.  
\v 6 Egha me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®z…®ma, kamagh…®n a d…®gavir kuram gami. 
\ms1 Iesus uan gavgavim suren gumazibar akaz…®, ez…® me deragha a g…®fozir pu 
\mr (Sapta 6:7-8:21) 
\s1 Iesus uan 12 plan aposelba ingangarim me ganighava me amada 
\r (Matyu 10:5-15 ko Luk 9:1-6) 
\p Egha Iesus nguibabagh aruava gumazamizibar sure gami.  
\v 7 Iesus men sure gamuava, egha 12 plan aposelbar diaz…®ma, me a bagha izez…®ma, a me akuvagha, me m…®g…®ava me amada. Gumazir pumuning uaning inigha zui, ez…® gumazir pumuning uaning inigha zui. A kamagh…®n amuava uaghan duar kuraba batozir gavgavim me ganigha me amada. 
\p  
\v 8-9 A m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam me gamuava me amada, ‚ÄúIa mang…®, bizir taba uari bagh da inian mark…®. Ia bret…®n tam ko m…®taritam inian mark…®. Ia dag…®atam suighan mark…®. Ia uan dagarir asuaba aghuva, ua siot…®n tam inian mark…®. Ia uan aghorir asadivibara suiragh mang…®.  
\v 10 Ia kamagh…®n damigh, mang…®va nguibatam…®n mang…®ght…® me d…®penitam ia danight…®, ia d…®penir kamra ik…®, mang…® dughiar ia nguibar kam ataghraghamim.  
\v 11 Ia kamagh…®n damu mang…® nguibatam…®n mang…®ght…®ma, me ian aghuagh ia inigh uan d…®penibar mang…®ghan kogh…®va, me uaghan ia m…®geir akaba baraghan koght…®ma, ia kamagh…®n damu. Ia nguibar kam ategh mang…®s…® uan dagarir m…®neziba ap…®sigh, egh nguibar kam ategh mang…®. Ia kamagh…®n damight…®, me ganigh fogham, me arazir aghuim ia gamizir puvat…®.‚Äù\f + \ft (6:11) Judabar arazim kara, n…® me baraghan koght…®ma, me n…®n sagh, uan dagarir asuaba m…®neziba ap…®zigh…®va n…® ategh igharagh mangam. Ez…® en arazim kamak…®n, k…® n…® m…®k…®mt…® n…® na baraghan koght…®, k…® apem ap…®righ uan tuavim gighuvagh, egh suam, k…® n…®n sagham.\f* 
\p  
\v 12 A kamagh…®n me m…®kemeghava me amadaz…®ma me nguibabar ghua God…®n akam akura ghaze, Ia uan navibagh iragh.  
\v 13 Me kamagh…®n me m…®g…®ava, egha uaghan gumazir av…®ribar duar kuraba batogha ar…®mariar gumazir av…®riba borem…®n men dapaniba ingiava me gamima, me ua dera. 
\s1 Herot Jon, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim…®n, f…®rim atu 
\r (Matyu 14:1-12 ko Luk 3:19-20 ko 9:7-9) 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Iesus bizir av…®ribagh amiz…®ma an ziam otogha ekevez…®ma, gumazir av…®riba a g…®fo. Ez…® danganir kam…®n atrivim, Herot, a baraki. Me marazi kamagh m…®gei, ‚ÄúJon Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim aremegha ua d…®kafi. Kamagh…®n a mirakelbar amuamin gavgavim iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® me marazi kamagh m…®gei, ‚ÄúA Elaija.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® marazi kamagh m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam, a mati fom…®ra ikezir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar m…®n ami.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Me akar kabav geima, Herot da baregha a fo, a fom…®ra Jon…®n f…®rim atu. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® fom…®ra m…®kemez…®ma, me gumazir mam Jon, Gumazibar Ruer Gumazim…®n f…®rim atuz…®ma, a ua d…®kafi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17-20 Herot kamagh…®n amigha a fo, a fom…®ra uan dozim Filip da an amuim Herodias a ini. Ez…® Jon zurara kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúHerot, na arazir kuram gamuava uan dozim da an amuim ini.‚Äù Jon kamagh m…®geima, Herodias a bagha guizbang…®ra navim isia, egha a Jon m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa a bagha puv…®ra Herot…®n m…®gei. Ez…® Herot Herodias ifongezir mogh…®n damuan aghuaghava, a uan gumazir mabav kemez…®ma me Jon…®n suiragha a inigha kalabus gat…®. Herot fo, Jon God…®n damazim…®n zuegha derazir gumazimra. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma Herot an atiatiava, a inigha deragha an gari. Herot uaghan Jon m…®geir akaba baragha n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amuava, ana akaba baraghasa ifonge. 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® Herodias dat…®r…®gh…®n Jon m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa tuavim bato. Herot an amebam a batezir dughiam otoz…®, a dughiar kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha isar ekiam gami. Herodias Jon…®n m…®soghamin dughiam dat…®r…®gh…®n oto. Herot isar kam gamuava, uan ingangarir ekiabar gari gumazir ekiaba, ko uan m…®dorozir gumazibar gari gumazir ekiaba, ko Galilin itir gumazir ekiaba, a men diaz…®ma me a ko damasa ize.  
\v 22 Me izegha isam apima Herodias…®n guivim izava me apir danganim…®n ghugha men guam…®n ighiam gami. A ighiam gamima, Herot ko izegha apir gumaziba ighiam…®n ganigha guizbang…®ra an ighiam gifongegha a bagha bar akonge. 
\p Me bar akuegha, egha Herot kamagh…®n guivir igiam m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® bizir manam gifongegh nan azaragh. Eght…® k…® bizir kam n…® danigam.‚Äù  
\v 23 A kamagh…®n a m…®kemegha, akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, n…® bizitam gifongegh, na m…®k…®m. N…® k…® garir bizibagh ifongegh…®va, na m…®k…®m. K…® tong…®ra da bigh…®va, taba n…® danigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 Guivir igiar kam akar kam baregha, azenan izegha ghua kamagh…®n uan amebam m…®gei, ‚ÄúAmebam, k…® bizir tizim bagh azaragham?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® an amebam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúJon, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim…®n, dapanim.‚Äù  
\v 25 Ez…® guivir kam akar kam baregha, zuam…®ra uamategha aven ghugha kamagh…®n Herot m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® dat…®r…®gh…®ra Jon, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim…®n, dapanim itaritam dat…®gh na dan…®ngigh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® Herot a bareghava navim bar oseme. A faragha akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim m…®geima a ko apir gumaziba a baraki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, an an azangs…®zim pueghan kogham.  
\v 27 Egha Herot a baraghav…®ra, akar gavgavim uan m…®dorozir gumazim m…®kemegha anemadaz…®ma a ghuava kalabus…®n aven iraghugha Jon…®n f…®rim atu.  
\v 28 A Jon…®n f…®rim atugha an dapanim inigha itarir mam gat…®gha a inigha izava guivir kam gan…®ngiz…®ma anenigha ghua uan amebam gan…®ngi.  
\v 29 Ez…® Jon…®n suren gumaziba an ovevem baregha izava an kuam inigha ghuava a mozim gat…®. 
\s1 Iesus dagheba 5,000…®n gumazibagh an…®di 
\r (Matyu 14:13-21 ko Luk 9:10-17 ko Jon 6:1-13) 
\p  
\v 30 Ez…® Iesus…®n aposelba ua izegha an borogh…®n uari akufa. Egha me aruava amizir biziba ko akar gumazibar sure gamizibar gun Iesus m…®gei.  
\v 31 Dughiar kam gumazamizir av…®riba me bagha iza zuima, me damamin dughiaba puvat…®. Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uarira na ko mang…®va gumaziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n mang…®va avughsam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 32 A kamagh…®n me m…®g…®ava egha me uarira bot inigha gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganir mam…®n zui.  
\v 33 Me zuima, gumazamizir av…®riba men ganigha me g…®fo. Ez…® nguibabar itir gumazamiziba bar men faraghav…®ra ivegha ghuava me zuir danganim…®n otifi.  
\v 34 Ez…® me ghuava dadarim…®n ghuegha Iesus gumazamizir av…®ribar garima, me guizbang…®ra bar av…®raseme. A men garima, me sipsipbar m…®n ami, me ghuaviba puvat…®, me pura asaghasazibar m…®n arui. A kamagh…®n bar men apangkufi. Egha a bizir av…®riba men sure gami.\f + \ft (6:34) N…® sipsip…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f* 
\p  
\v 35 A m…®g…®av…®ra itima, am…®nim p…®riz…®ma an suren gumaziba a bagha izava kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganim, ez…® am…®nim p…®ri.  
\v 36 N…® gumazamiziba amadaght…®, me mang…® danganir kam…®n itir nguibaba ko rogh…®ra itir nguibar dozibar mang…®va me dam…®s…® uari bagh daghebagh ives.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 37 Ez…® a me ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uari daghetaba me dan…®ng.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúDag…®ar e me bagh bretbagh ivezamim, a 200 Kinan tu. E da inigh, mang…®, me bagh bretbagh ivezegh me dan…®ngasa, n…® ifonge?‚Äù\f + \ft (6:37) Grigh…®n akam kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, gumazim bretba kamagh…®n ives…®va, an 8 plan iakinibar ingarigham.\f* 
\p  
\v 38 Ez…® Iesus men azara, ‚ÄúIa manmagh…®ra bretba iti? Ia mang…® ganigh.‚Äù A m…®kemez…®, me ghua ganigha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE bret…®n 5 pla koma osirir pumuning kati.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 39 Ez…® Iesus me m…®kemez…® me gumazamizibav geima, me uari uari tuiragha grazim gapia.  
\v 40 Ez…® me uari tuiragha apia, marazi 50, marazi 100…®n ghu.  
\v 41 Me apiaghav itima, ez…® Iesus bret…®n 5 pla inigha, osirir pumuning inigha, p…®n overiam…®n garava God m…®nabagha bretba ab…®aghar…®ki. Egha uan suren gumazibav geima, me da isa, gumazamizibagh an…®di. A uaghan osirimning sara b…®aghar…®ghiz…®ma, me da isa, me gan…®di.  
\v 42 Ez…® gumazamizir kaba bar amegha, naviba bar iz…®fa.  
\v 43 Men naviba bar iz…®vaz…®ma Iesus…®n suren gumaziba, dagher nar me ataghiziba, me da inigha ak…®rar 12 pla gaghuiz…®ma, da bar iz…®fa.  
\v 44 Dagheba amezir gumazibara, men av…®rim 5,000…®n tu. 
\s1 Iesus d…®pam gis…®n tugha zui 
\r (Matyu 14:22-36 ko Jon 6:16-21) 
\p  
\v 45 Gumazamiziba dagheba amez…®ma, ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibar ariragha ghaze, Ia bot…®n b…®nigh…®va faragh Betsaidan vong…®n nguibam…®n mang…®. K…® uab…®ra ik…®va gumazamiziba amadaght…®ma me ua uan nguibabar mangam.  
\v 46 A me amadaz…®, me ghuez…®ma, ez…® a God ko m…®k…®masa m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuavanabo. 
\p  
\v 47 Dughiar kam am…®nim p…®rima, men bot d…®pam…®n tong…®n itima, Iesus uab…®ra dadarim…®n iti.  
\v 48 A ikiava uan suren gumazibar garima, am…®nir gavgavim izava men bot g…®vai. Me pul gamua ingangarir dafam gamuava am…®nim ko uari adosi. Egha am…®nim tiasava amima, Iesus d…®pam gis…®n tugha me bagha zui. A mang…® me gitagh mangasa.  
\v 49-50 Ez…® me an garima, a d…®pam gis…®n tugha zuima, me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúKar ti asetam.‚Äù 
\p Me n…®ghn…®zir kam gamuava, bar an ganigha puv atiatiava arai. Me araima, a zuam…®ra kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gavgafigh, kar k…®rara. Ia atiatingan mark…®!‚Äù  
\v 51-52 A kamagh…®n me m…®g…®ava, me gat…®n bot…®n aven ghuz…®ma, am…®nim pura dutugha ghu. Ez…® me bizir kam, Iesus 5,000…®n gumaziba bretba me gan…®ngiz…®, me damez…®, me ganigha, kamagh…®n me tong bar fozir puvat…®. Men n…®ghn…®ziba otefe. Egha bizir kabagh n…®ghn…®ghava guizbang…®ra d…®gavir kuram gami.\f + \ft (6:52) Dughiar kam…®n Iesus bret gumazamizibagh an…®gava, uan gavgavim men akakasi, me kamagh…®n ganigh suam, a bizir bar av…®rir igharagha garibar amuamin gavgavim iti. Ez…®ma an suren gumaziba bizir kabar garava a dagh fozir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n me Iesus…®n garima a d…®pam gis…®n aruava am…®nim gamiz…®ma an am…®raz…®ma me ganighava d…®gavir kuram gami.\f* 
\p  
\v 53 Egha Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko d…®pam…®n vong…®n ghugha, ghua Genesaret…®n nguibam…®n otivigha, bot ike.  
\v 54 Me bot ikegha dadarim…®n anadima, gumazamiziba Iesus…®n garav…®ra a g…®fo.  
\v 55 Me a g…®fogha, egha gumazamiziba Iesus itir danganim baregha, ivegha danganir kam garuava uan ar…®mariar gumaziba inigha me akuriabagh arigha me inigha Iesus bagha izi.  
\v 56 Iesus nguibar ekiaba ko nguibar doziba ko ruarir nguibaba dar zui. A zuir nguibar kaba me arazir kamram ami, me ar…®mariar gumaziba inigha izava nguibam…®n tong…®n da ar…®gha, egha me a gakaghora ghaze, a men asught…®ma, ar…®mariaba itiba an korotiar av…®zibar suigham. Ez…® gumazamizir an korotiam…®n suiziba, men ar…®mariaba gefi. 
\c 7  
\s1 God…®n araziba Judan ovavibar arazibagh afira. 
\r (Matyu 15:1-9) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Farisin gumazir maba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumazir maba, me Jerusalem…®n ikegha, izaghrava, Iesus bagha izava anekufa.  
\v 2 Me iza ikia garima, Iesus…®n suren gumazir maba men ovavibar arazibar g…®n ghuava dafariba ruegha dagheba apir puvat…®. Me pura dagheba api.  
\v 3 Farisin kaba koma Judan gumazamiziba bar, me uan ovavibar arazibar suighav…®ra ikiava, me dafariba ruava api. Me pura daghebar aman kogham.  
\v 4 Me uaghan maket…®n inigha izir dagheba, me dar aman kogham. Me faragh da ruegh egh dar amam. Me uaghan uan ovavibar arazir av…®rir maba sara suiraghav…®ra iti. Me pura dagheba isamigh dameghan kogham. Me faragh uan m…®neba ko itariba ko apir dakoziba, ruegh…®va egh me dagheba isamam. 
\p  
\v 5 Kamagh…®n, Farisiba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba, me Iesus…®n azara, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n amiz…® n…®n suren gumaziba en ovavibar arazibar g…®n mang…® dafariba ruan aghuagha, pura dagheba api?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Iesus me ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uarira uarigh ifarir gumazibara. God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Aisaia, a guizbang…®ra ia amir arazibar gun m…®g…®ava kamagh…®n osiri, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄòGumazamizir kaba, me uan akatoribar nan ziam fe, 
\q2 egha men naviba ko n…®ghn…®ziba bar saghon iti. 
\q1  
\v 7 Me gumazibar akabar uari sure gamua uari gifara egha ghaze, kar God…®n akam. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me nan ziam guizbang…®ra a fer puvat…®.‚Äô 
\b  
\m  
\v 8 Ia kamagh…®n amua, God…®n akaba, ia da ategha, uan ovavibar araziba, dar suiragha gavgafi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 A m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa ghaze, ia arazir aghuim gamua God…®n akaba ategha uan arazibar g…®n zui. Ian arazir kaba bar ikufi.  
\v 10 Moses fom…®ra kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄòIa uan afeziaba ko amebabar akaba baregh men apengan ik…®va, egh gumazitam akar kuratam uan afeziam ko amebam m…®kemeght…®, ia gumazir kam m…®sueght…®, an aremegh.‚Äô  
\v 11 Ez…® ia kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòGumazitam uan amebam ko afeziam…®n akurvaghs…® dag…®aba at…®gha, egha ua g…®n aning…®n akuraghan aghuagha, kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGuan akuraghasa at…®zir dag…®aba, gua mark…®. K…® da is…® God dan…®ngam.‚Äù ‚Äô  
\v 12 Ia kamagh…®n m…®geima, gumazir kam bizitam uan amebam ko afeziam…®n akuravazir puvat…®.  
\v 13 Ia kamagh…®n amuava, uan ovaviba da inizir arazibar g…®n ghuava, da gumazir igharazibagh an…®di. Ian arazir kabar, ia God…®n araziba ategha, uan ovavibar araziba faragha dar…®si. Egha God…®n akam gami a mati pura bizim. Ia amir bizir av…®rir maba uaghan iti.‚Äù 
\s1 God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezir biziba, Iesus dav gei 
\r (Matyu 15:10-20) 
\p  
\v 14 Egha Iesus ua uab…®n borogh…®n itir gumazamizibar diaz…®ma, me a bagha izima, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa bar na baragh…®va egh nan akar kaba, deraghv…®ra dagh fogh.  
\v 15-16 Bizitam azenan ikegha gumazim…®n navim…®n aven magir…® an navir averiam damight…®, a God…®n damazim…®n m…®zeghan kogham. puvat…®, gumazim…®n navim…®n aven ikegha azenan izezir biziba, an navir averiam damight…®ma, a God…®n damazim…®n m…®zegham.‚Äù \f + \ft (7:15-16) Bizir apiba azenan ikegha ghuaghira gumazim…®n muriar averiam gamima a God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezir puvat…®. Ez…® bizir kurar navim…®n aven ikegha azenan iziba a gamima an navir averiam m…®ze.\f* 
\p  
\v 17 Iesus akar kaba gumazamizir av…®ribav kemegha, me ategha ghua d…®penim…®n aven ghuz…®ma, an suren gumaziba akar is…®n zuim…®n m…®ngarim bagha an azara.  
\v 18-19 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúEee! Ia ongani? Ia uaghan akar kam derav…®ra a g…®fozir puvat…®? Ia bizir kam g…®fo? Daghetam guizbang…®ra gumazim…®n navir averiam…®n mag…®r…®gh ikeghan kogham. Da an navim…®n aven mag…®r…®gh, egh an muriam…®n mag…®r…®ght…®ma a g…®n dar aviam. Kamagh…®n gumazim apir bizitam azenan ikegh an akam ko muriam…®n mag…®r…®gh, an muriam damight…®ma a God…®n damazim…®n m…®zeghan kogham.‚Äù (Iesus…®n akar gavgavim kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, dagheba bar God…®n damazim…®n bar zue. Ez…® e dar amam.) 
\p  
\v 20 A m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazim…®n navim…®n aven ikegha azenan izezir biziba, an arazir kuraba, a gamima, an navim God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze.  
\v 21 Gumazim…®n navim…®n aven ikegha azenan izezir arazibar kara, n…®ghn…®zir kuraba, gumazamiziba tintinba uari koma akui, biziba okei, gumazibav m…®sozi da ariagh…®ri,  
\v 22 poroghamiba uari bakei, m…®gh…®v…®ra bizibagh ifonge, gumazir igharazibagh as…®ghas…®ghasa n…®ghn…®si, ifavariba, aghums…®ziba puvat…®zir arazir kuraba, bizim bagha navim ikufi, gumazir igharazim…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®si, uab…®ra uab…® fe, arazir onganiba,  
\v 23 arazir kurar kaba bar navim…®n aven ikegha azenan iza, gumazim gamima a God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze.‚Äù 
\s1 Fonisian amizim n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n iti 
\r (Matyu 15:21-28) 
\p  
\v 24 Egha Iesus Genesaret ategha Tair…®n nguibar ekiam…®n danganim…®n ghu. A gumazamiziba a g…®foghan an aghuagha, egha mogomebar ghua d…®penir mam…®n aven ghugha egha modozir puvat…®. Me bar fo, a d…®penim…®n aven iti.  
\v 25 A d…®penir kam…®n itima, guivir duar kuram apazazim…®n amebam, a Iesus izezir darorim baregha, zuam…®ra a bagha izava an dagarimning ir…®.  
\v 26 Amizir kam, an amebam Fonisian Distrigh…®n a bate. Sirian danganir ekiam…®n aven itir distrigh. Ez…® a Grigh…®n akam…®n m…®gei. A duar kurar an guivim gapazazim batoghasa Iesus m…®g…®ava a gakaghori. 
\p  
\v 27 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE faragh boribar dagheba me dan…®ngt…®, me damam. Arazir kuram, k…® boribar dagheba inigh afiabav k…®nam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® amizim kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir Ekiam, k…® fo, afiaba uaghan boribar dakozim…®n apengan irezir dagher muzuemziariba api.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am dera. Kamagh…®n n…® uamategh…®va uan d…®penim…®n mang…®. Duar kurar kam n…®n guivim ategha azenan ize.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 30 Ez…® a uamategha uan d…®penim…®n ghuava garima, an guivim uan dakozim gir…®ghav iti. Ez…® an an ganigha fo, duar kurar kam an ategha azenan ghu. 
\s1 Iesus gumazir kuarir onganir mam…®n akuraz…® a dera. 
\p  
\v 31 Ez…® Iesus d…®kavigha Tair…®n danganim ategha, ghua Saidon…®n danganim…®n otogha ghua, Dikapolis…®n Distrigh…®n otogha ghua, Galilin d…®pam…®n dadarim giraghu.  
\v 32 A ghuz…®ma, gumazir maba gumazir kuarir onganir mam inigha Iesus bagha izi. A uaghan m…®zem osemegha derav…®ra m…®geir puvat…®. Me izegha dafarim a dar…®ghasa Iesus gakaghori. 
\p  
\v 33 Ez…® Iesus gumazir kam inigha gumazir av…®riba ategha aning uaningra m…®riam…®n ghugha, egha a uan akakazir dafarimning gumazim…®n kuarimning gat…®gha aning asigha, egha iparigha, an m…®zem…®n suira.  
\v 34 Egha Iesus p…®n overiam…®n garava, gumazir kam bagha navim bigha arava kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEfata!‚Äù (Akar kam…®n m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu, ‚ÄúKuighr…®gh!‚Äù)  
\v 35 Iesus kamagh…®n m…®g…®av…®ra itima, an kuarimning kuiaghir…®. Ez…® an m…®zem m…®gh…®vgh…®ki. Ez…® a derav…®ra bizibav gei. 
\p  
\v 36 Ez…® Iesus akar gavgavim…®n bizir kam…®n gun m…®k…®man men anogoroke. A men anogoroghez…®ma me ua puv…®rama bizir kam…®n gun m…®g…®av…®ra iti.  
\v 37 Me akar kam m…®geima, gumazamizir kaba a baregha guizbang…®ra d…®gavir kuram gamigha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir kam an amir biziba da bar dera. A kuarir onganibagh amima, me uam orasi. Egha, m…®zer os…®mt…®zibagh amima, me ua derav…®ra bizibav gei.‚Äù 
\c 8  
\s1 Iesus 4,000…®n gumaziba dagheba me gan…®di 
\r (Matyu 15:32-39; 16:1-4) 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar kam gumazamizir av…®rir igharaziba uari akufa. Me damamin dagheba puvat…®. Ez…® kamagh…®n Iesus uan suren gumazibar diaz…® me a bagha izima a kamagh…®n me m…®gei,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúGumazamizir kaba, me na ko aruer pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n ikia, egha dagheba puvat…®gha m…®tiriam men azi, kamagh…®n k…® men apangkufi.  
\v 3 Me marazi saghon kegha ize. Kamagh…®n k…® me amadaght…®, me m…®tiriaba sara, uan nguibabar mang…®va damaziba men isirt…®ma me iram.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® an suren gumaziba an akam ikara, ‚ÄúE managh gumaziba itir puvat…®zir danganir kam…®n tina bret…®n av…®riba inigh me dan…®ngam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Me kamagh…®n m…®geima Iesus kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúIa manmagh bretba iti?‚Äù Me a ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚Äú7 pla.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Iesus nguazim…®n dapiasa gumazamizibav kemez…® me apia. Ez…® a 7 pla bretba inigha God m…®nabagha egha da b…®agharigha, gumazamizibar an…®ngasa uan suren gumazibagh an…®ngiz…®ma me me gan…®di. 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® me uaghan osirir muziarir maba iti. Ez…® a uaghan da bagha God m…®nabagha da me dan…®ngasa uan suren gumazibav gei.  
\v 8 Gumazamizir av…®riba me amegha bar iz…®fa. Ez…® g…®n suren gumaziba dagher nar me taghiziba, me da inigha 7 pla ak…®rabagh aghuiz…®ma, da iz…®fa.  
\v 9 Dughiar kam…®n itir gumazamizibar d…®bobonim 4,000…®n borogh…®n ghu. Me amez…®ma, a me amadaz…®, me uan nguibabar ghue.  
\v 10 Me zuima, a uan suren gumaziba koma bot…®n b…®nigha, Daramanutan danganim…®n ghue. 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Farisiba izegha ifavarir azangs…®zibar Iesus gami. Eght…®, God gavgavim a danight…®, a mirakel…®n arazitam damight…®, me ganigh fogh suam, God guizbang…®ra anemada.  
\v 12 Ez…® a men azangs…®zir ifavaribar am…®ragha ghuariaba suegha, egha me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa dat…®r…®gh…®n itir gumazamizir kaba tizim bagha mirakel…®n arazim bagha nan azangs…®si? K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, God mirakel…®n arazitam ian akaghan kogham.‚Äù  
\v 13 Egha a me ategha uamategha bot…®n b…®ragha, egha d…®pam…®n vong…®n ghu. 
\s1 Farisiba ko Herot…®n yis…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Matyu 16:5-12) 
\p  
\v 14 Egha me ghuava Iesus…®n suren gumaziba bretba bak…®n…®gh…®nigha ize. Me bret…®n vam…®ra iniz…®ma a me ko bot…®n iti.  
\v 15 Ez…® Iesus akar gavgavim…®n kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa deragh uari bagh gan! Ia derav…®ra Farisibar yis ko Herot…®n yis bagh derav…®ra gan.‚Äù \f + \ft (8:15) N…® yis…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f* 
\p  
\v 16 Iesus me m…®kemez…®ma, me kamagh…®n uarira uariv gei, ‚ÄúE bret tam inigha izezir puvat…®z…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®ma an e m…®gei.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Me uarira uariv geima, Iesus men m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh fogha kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha ghaze, e bret tam inigha izezir puvat…®? Eee, ia k…® amir bizibar garava, fozir puvat…®. Ia t…®ghar deraghv…®ra dagh fofogham? Ian n…®ghn…®ziba bar otefe.  
\v 18 Ia damaziba ikia, garir puvat…®? Ia kuariba ikia, orazir puvat…®? Ia bizir kabagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®?  
\v 19 Ia, k…® bret…®n 5 pla b…®agharigha ia gan…®ngiz…®ma, ia 5,000…®n gumazibagh an…®ngiz…®ma, me da apa iz…®vagha, ataghizir naba ia da ak…®raba manmagh…®n aghui?‚Äù Me kamagh…®n a ikara, ‚ÄúE 12 pla ak…®rabagh aghui.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® a ua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúEz…® k…® bret…®n 7 pla b…®agharigha ia gan…®ngiz…®ma, ia 4,000…®n gumazamizibagh an…®ngiz…®ma, me da apa iz…®vaz…® ia dar naba ak…®raba manmagh…®n aghui?‚Äù 
\p Me kamagh…®n a ikara, ‚ÄúE 7 pla ak…®rabagh aghui.‚Äù  
\v 21 Me kamagh…®n a m…®geima, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúEee, ia t…®ghar bizibagh fofogham.‚Äù 
\ms1 Iesus uan suren gumazibar sure gami 
\mr (Sapta 8:22-10:52) 
\s1 Iesus Betsaidan gumazir damazir kurar mam…®n akuraz…®, an damazimning ua dera 
\p  
\v 22 Egha me Betsaidan ghuez…®ma, gumazir maba gumazir damazir kurar mam inigha, Iesus bagha izi. Me izegha dafarim a dar…®ghasava Iesus gakaghori.  
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus gumazir damazir kuram…®n agharim…®n suiragha, a inigha nguibam ategha azenan ghu. Aning azenan ghugha, egha Iesus gumazim…®n damazimning giparigha uan dafarimning a gis…®n at…®gha kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúN…® bizitam…®n gari?‚Äù  
\v 24 Ez…® gumazir kam kogha garava kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAre, k…® garima, gumaziba temebar m…®n garav arui.‚Äù  
\v 25 Ez…® Iesus ua uan dafarimning an damazimning…®n suiraz…®ma, gumazim…®n damazimning kuiaghr…®z…®ma, a ua deragha bizibar gari.  
\v 26 Ez…® Iesus anemaga kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ua nguibar kam…®n aven mangan mark…®. N…® uan d…®penim…®n mang…®.‚Äù 
\s1 Pita Iesus…®n gun m…®gei 
\r (Matyu 16:13-20 ko Luk 9:18-21) 
\p  
\v 27 Egha Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko d…®kavigha Sisaria Filipain nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n itir nguibar dozibar zui. Me ghuava a tuavim…®n men azara, ‚ÄúGumazamiziba tina na gar…®si?‚Äù  
\v 28 Me a ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúMarazi ghaze, n…® Jon, Gumaziba Ruer Gumazim. Ez…® marazi ghaze, n…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elaija. Ez…® marazi ghaze, n…® fom…®ra ikezir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúEz…® ia? Ia tina na gar…®si?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Pita kamagh…®n a ikara, ‚ÄúN…® Krais, God Ua e Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 30 Ez…® Iesus akar gavgavim…®n kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa nan gun gumazitam m…®k…®man mark…® suam, k…® tina.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus uan ovevem ko ua d…®kavamin m…®g…®r…®g…®am gami 
\r (Matyu 16:21-28 ko Luk 9:22-27) 
\p  
\v 31 Egha Iesus men sure gamuava kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazibar Otarim bar m…®zazir ekiaba koma os…®mt…®ziba iniam. Eght…®ma gumazir aruaba, koma ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, koma Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba, me an aghuagh…®va a m…®sueght…®ma an aremegham. Egh dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim g…®vaght…® a ua d…®kavigham.‚Äù  
\v 32 Iesus kamagh…®n uan ovevem aghurigha me m…®geima, ez…® Pita a inigha m…®riam…®n ghugha, an atarava kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 33 A kamagh…®n m…®geima, Iesus ragha uan suren gumazibar garava, Pitan atarava kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúSatan, n…® na gitagh mang…®! N…® nguazim…®n bizibagh n…®ghn…®gha egha God…®n bizibagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 34 Egha Iesus gumazamiziba ko uan suren gumazibar, diaz…®ma, me a bagha izima, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam nan g…®n iz…®s…®, a ifongezir biziba g…®n amadagh uan temer ighuvim gisaghpugh nan g…®n iz…®.  
\v 35 Gumazir manam uan ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n suiraghs…® n…®ghn…®ght…®, an ik…®r…®m…®rim g…®vagham. Eght…® gumazir manam akar aghuim ko na bagh uan ik…®r…®m…®rim ategh…®va, a uan ik…®r…®m…®rim iniam.  
\v 36 Gumazitam nguazim…®n itir biziba bar da iniva, egh a g…®n oveght…®, bizir kaba manmagh…®n an akuragham? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 37 A ivezir manam uan duam bagh aneren…®ngam? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 38 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n itir gumazamiziba me God ak…®rim ragha a gasaragha arazir kurabagh ami. Men tina nan ziam ko nan akar aghuim…®n gun m…®k…®man aghums…®ght…® g…®n Gumazibar Otarim uan afeziam…®n borogh…®n ikegh…®va God…®n damazim…®n zuezir enselba koma God…®n angazangarim sara izighir…®va, uaghan men aghums…®gham.‚Äù 
\c 9  
\p  
\v 1 Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia kagh tuivighav itir darasi, ian tarazi oveghan kogham. Ia ik…®v…®ra ik…® gant…®ma, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam gavgavim sara izighram.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus…®n m…®karzim igharagha oto 
\r (Matyu 17:1-13 ko Luk 9:28-36) 
\p  
\v 2 Ez…® dughiar 6 pla g…®vaz…®ma, Iesus Pita koma Jems ko Jon me inigha m…®ghs…®ar ekiam…®n ghuavanabogha, me uarira kagh iti. A kagh an m…®karzim men damazim…®n igharaghav oto.  
\v 3 An korotiabar angazangarir gavgavir kam guizbang…®ra ghurghuri. Ghurghurir kam nguazim…®n gumazitam ruezir bizir ghurghuritam an m…®n garir puvat…®.  
\v 4 Ez…® me garima Elaija ko Moses otogha Iesus ko me uariv gei.\f + \ft (9:4) Moses ko Elaija bar fom…®ram ovengez…®ma, Iesus bogh…®mra nguazir kam…®n ize.\f* 
\p  
\v 5-6 Me uariv g…®av…®ra itima, Pita, Jems ko Jon me bar atiatigha, Pita m…®k…®mamin m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh asagha pura kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, bar deragha e kagh iti! E averpenir pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n ingaram. N…® bagh tam, Moses bagh tam, egh Elaija bagh tam.‚Äù  
\v 7 Ez…® ghuariam otogha me avaraz…®ma ez…® tiarir mam ghuariam…®n tong…®n otogha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar nan Otarir k…® bar ifongezim. Ia anar…®ram oragh!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Egha zuam…®ra me gara ua gumazitam…®n garir puvat…®. Iesus uab…®ra me ko iti. 
\p  
\v 9 Egha me uamategha m…®ghs…®am…®n izaghrava Iesus bizir otozir me ganizim…®n gun gumazitam m…®k…®man bar men anogoroke. Kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® Gumazibar Otarim aremegh ua d…®kavigham.  
\v 10 Me ganizir bizir kam merara itima, ez…® me aremegh ua d…®kavighamin m…®g…®r…®g…®ar m…®ngarim bagha uarira uariv gei. 
\p  
\v 11 Egha me an azara, ‚ÄúManmagh sua Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ghaze, Elaija faragh izeght…®, God Ua e Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim g…®n izam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® Iesus men azangs…®zim ikara, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra Elaija faragh izegh…®va bizibar ak…®ram. Ez…® tizim bagha fom…®ra God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n osizirim kamagh…®n iti, ‚ÄòGumazibar Otarim os…®mt…®zir av…®ribar aven mang…®t…® me ak…®rim a gasaragham?‚Äô  
\v 13 Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, Elaija izegha g…®fa. Ez…® gumazamiziba ak…®nafarim…®n osizirir an gun m…®kemezim…®n m…®rara, me uan arazir me ifongezibar a gami.‚Äù \f + \ft (9:13) Dughiar kam…®n Iesus Elaija izamin bizim m…®gei, egha guizbang…®ra Jon, Gumaziba ruer gumazim m…®gei. N…® foghs…®, Matyu 17:12…®n gan. Jon izava Iesus izasava a bagha tuavibar ak…®ra faragha ize.\f* 
\s1 Iesus otarir duar kuram apazazim gamiz…®ma a ua dera 
\r (Matyu 17:14-23 ko Luk 9:37-45) 
\p  
\v 14 Egha me iza suren gumazir maba bativigha garima gumazamizir av…®rim me akuvaz…® Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba me ko uariv g…®a uari adosi.  
\v 15 Me uari adozima gumazamiziba Iesus…®n garav…®ra d…®gavir kuram gamigha dughiam a dan…®ngasa ivegha zui.  
\v 16 Egha a kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha me ko ia uari adosi?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® gumazir mam gumazamizir av…®rim…®n torim…®n ikiava kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, k…® uan otarim inigha n…® bagha ize, duar kuram a gapazaz…®ma, a m…®geir puvat…®.  
\v 18 Egha an a gamir dughiam…®n, an anekurima a daghira, pupuviba an akam m…®sevima an atariba uariv tivima a m…®k…®rvasi. K…® duar kuram batoghasa n…®n suren gumazibar azaraz…® me a batoghezir puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 19 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúOio! K…® bar am…®ra, dat…®r…®gh…®n itir gumazamiziba n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba puvat…®. K…® fom…®ra ia ko itima, ia dazogh…®n bizitam g…®fogham? K…® dughiabar zurara ian os…®mt…®ziba ateram? Otarim inigh na bagh iz…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® me otarim Iesus bagha a inigha ize. Ez…®ma duar kuram Iesus…®n apigha, magh…®ra otarim gamima a n…®si. A nguazim gir…®gha poghpogha pupuviba an akam m…®sefi.  
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus otarim…®n afeziam…®n azara, ‚ÄúA man dughiam…®n duar kuram a gapasa?‚Äù Ez…® afeziam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAn agh…®rimra itima an a gapasa.  
\v 22 An a damight…® an aremeghasa dughiar av…®ribar anekurima an aviba ko d…®pabar ghuaghiri. N…® bizir kabar amuva, en apangkuvigh en akurvagh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uab…®! N…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…®t…® biziba bar deragham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 Ez…® otarim…®n afeziam zuam…®ra kamagh…®n diagha m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikiava, an otefe. Ez…® n…® nan akuragh!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 25 Egha Iesus garima gumazamiziba ivemara men borogh…®n zuima a duar kuram batogha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® duar kurar gumazibagh ami me orazi puvat…®zim ko m…®geir puvat…®zim, k…® n…® m…®gei, azenan iz…® egh uam aven mangan mark…®!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® duar kam aregha pamtem…®n a gunabagha azenan ize. Ez…® otarim gumazir kuam…®n m…®n gari, ez…® me bar kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAn areme.‚Äù  
\v 27 Ez…® Iesus an agharim…®n suiragha a ghufez…® a d…®kavigha tu. 
\p  
\v 28 Egha Iesus d…®penim…®n aven ghuz…®ma an suren gumaziba mogomem…®n kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúManmagh amiz…®, e duar kurar kam batoghava avenge?‚Äù  
\v 29 Ez…® a kamagh…®n me ikara, ‚ÄúDuar kurar kamagh…®n amiba God ko m…®geir arazim…®n gavgavim…®n azenan izi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 30-31 Egha me danganir kam ategha Galilin Distrigh…®n otogha zui. Me ghuava Iesus uan suren gumazibar sure gami. Bizir kam…®n Iesus me iti nagh…®n gumazitam foghan an aghua. Me ghua, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe Gumazibar Otarim is…®va gumazibar dafarim dar…®gham. Eght…® me a m…®sueght…® an ovegham. Eght…® dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim g…®vaght…® a ua d…®kavigham.‚Äù  
\v 32 Ez…® me m…®g…®r…®g…®ar a m…®kemezim a g…®fozir puvat…®gha, egha a bagha an azangs…®ghan atiatingi. 
\s1 Tinarama Ekiam 
\r (Matyu 18:1-5 ko Luk 9:46-48) 
\p  
\v 33 Egha me Kaperneam…®n izegha d…®penim…®n aven ikia Iesus men azara, ‚ÄúIa tuavim…®n tizim m…®g…®a uari batosi?‚Äù  
\v 34 Me tuavim…®n tinara ekiam, a m…®g…®r…®g…®am gamua uari batoke. Kamagh…®n me n…®m…®ra iti.  
\v 35 Egha Iesus aperaghav ikiava suren gumazir 12 plan diagha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTina faragh ik…®s…®, a bar g…®n kegh egh gumaziba bar men ingarir gumazim…®n otogh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 36 Egha a borir dozim inigha me uan tong…®n anefaz…® a tughav iti. Egha a uan agharimning a muigha kamagh…®n me m…®gei,  
\v 37 ‚ÄúGumazitam na g…®n…®ghn…®gh egh borir dozir kamagh garitam inigh an akuragham, kamagh…®n a na inigha nan akurvasi. Egha n…® tina nan akurvasi, n…® na gamir puvat…®. N…® uaghan gumazir na amadazim gami.‚Äù 
\s1 Tina en apanim gami puvat…® a enanav 
\r (Luk 9:49-50) 
\p  
\v 38 Egha Jon kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, e garima gumazir mam duar kurabar n…®n ziam…®n da batosi. E fo, a en mav puvat…®, ez…®ma e an anogorosi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 39 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAn anogoroghan mark…®. Gumazitam nan ziam…®n mirakel damigh, egh dughiar igharazim akar kuraba na damighan kogham.  
\v 40 Tina en apanim gami puvat…® a enanav.  
\v 41 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia Gumazir God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezim…®n adarasi. Kamagh…®n tina nan ziam…®n d…®patam ia daning…®va a guizbang…®ra uan ivezim iniam.‚Äù 
\s1 Arazir kuraba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim gas…®ghas…®si 
\r (Matyu 18:6-9 ko Luk 17:1-2) 
\p  
\v 42 Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEgh…®va tina n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itir borir katam damight…® an arazir kuratam damight…®, a hel…®n mang…®va, a bar ivezir kuram inigham. Kamagh…®n dera, me dag…®ar ekiam an f…®rim dafagh…®va ongarim m…®k…®night…® an aremegham.  
\v 43-44 Egh n…®n agharim n…® damight…® na arazir kuratam damigh…®va, anetugh. Kamagh…®n dera, n…® agharir vam…®ra ik…®va zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim…®n aven mangam. N…® agharir pumuning v…®rara ik…®va hel…®n mangam, nguibar avim mungemari puvat…®zim.  
\v 45-46 Egh n…®n suem n…® damight…® na arazir kuratam damigh…®va, anetugh. Kamagh…®n dera, n…® suer vam…®ra ik…®va zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim…®n aven mangam. N…® suer pumuning v…®rara ik…®t…® me n…® is…®va hel…®n n…® akunigham.  
\v 47 Egh n…®n damatuzim n…® damut…® na arazir kuratam damigh…®va anesigh. Kamagh…®n dera, n…® damazir vam…®ra ik…®va God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven mangam. N…® damazimning v…®rara ik…®t…®, God n…® is…®va hel…®n n…® akunigham.  
\v 48 Danganir kam 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄòApizir nguzir men m…®karziba apiba g…®vaghan kogham. 
\q2 Ez…® men m…®karziba isir avim uaghan mungueghan kogham.‚Äô 
\b  
\p  
\v 49 ‚ÄúGumaziba ofa God dan…®ngasa, me amangs…®zim ofa gamir daghebagh ar…®gha avim…®n da tuava da isa, egha God gan…®di. Amangs…®zim koma avim ofa gamir daghebagh amima da God…®n damazim…®n zue. Kamagh…®ra os…®mt…®ziba gumazamiziba bativam. Egh me damut…®, me God…®n damazim…®n zuegham. \f + \ft (9:49-50) Ves 49 ko 50…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®riba aning…®n aven iti. Ez…®ma Grigh…®n akam deragha dar akar m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Ez…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam fofozir gumaziba uaghan n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ram an itir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 50 Amangs…®zim a dera, egh a uan s…®ngt…®zim ateght…®, n…® manmagh…®n a damight…® a ua s…®ngigham? Ia amangs…®zim inigh uari dat…®gh, egh ia uari ko navir am…®r…®zim…®n ik…®.‚Äù 
\c 10  
\s1 Poroghamiba uari ataghrasi 
\r (Matyu 19:1-12 ko Luk 16:18) 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Iesus nguibar kam ategha ghua, Judian Distrigh…®n ghua Jordan…®n d…®pam…®n vong…®n oto. An otoz…®ma, gumazamizir av…®riba ua izava, anekuvaz…®ma, a zurara ami mogh…®n men sure gami. 
\p  
\v 2 A men sure gamima, Farisin maba izava a gifarava kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúN…® e m…®k…®m, en arazim manmagh…®n m…®gei? Gumazim uan amuim ateghamin arazir kam deras, ti puvat…®?‚Äù  
\v 3 A men azangs…®zim ikaragha kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúMoses arazir manam damuasa ia m…®keme?‚Äù  
\v 4 Ez…® me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúMoses, gumazitam amuim ateghs…® poroghamning uaning ataghraghamin ak…®nafarir av…®zim osirigh amizim amadaghasa, an e m…®keme.‚Äù  
\v 5 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me ikara, ‚ÄúIan naviba gavgafi, kamagh…®n amiz…®ma Moses ia bagha arazir kam osiri.  
\v 6 Bar fom…®ra God nguazir kam ko biziba bar dagh amuav…®ra gumaziba ko amizibagh ami.  
\v 7 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, gumazim uan afeziam ko amebam ategh…®va, a uan amuim ko aning uaning…®n porogham.  
\v 8 Egh aning nivaf…®zir vam…®ram otogham. Aning ua gumazir pumuning puvat…®. Aning nivaf…®zir vam…®ra ikiam  
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma God bizir pumuning isafuraght…®ma, gumazitam aning abighan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Egha me uamategha d…®penim…®n aven ghua, Iesus…®n suren gumaziba bizir kam bagha an azara.  
\v 11 A me ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam uan amuim ategh amizir igharazim…®n ik…®va, gumazir kam uan amuim gas…®ghas…®gha poroghamiba uari bak…®a uari isava akuir arazim gami.  
\v 12 Ez…® amizitam uan pam ategh gumazir igharazim…®n ik…®va, amizir kam poroghamiba uari bak…®a uari isava akuir arazim gami.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus boriba ko 
\r (Matyu 19:13-15 ko Luk 18:15-17) 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® gumazamiziba borir doziba inigha Iesus bagha izi. Eght…® a uan dafarimning me gis…®n dar…®ghasa me izima, an suren gumaziba men atarava men anogorosi.  
\v 14 Me men atarima, Iesus men ganigha navim an ikuviz…®ma, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tina God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven ik…®s…®, borir dozir kabar m…®n ik…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma borir doziba ateght…®ma, me na bagh iz…®. Men anogoroghan mark…®.  
\v 15 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, gumazitam borir dozir kabar m…®n God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam inighan kogh…®va, egh an aven mangan bar iburagham.‚Äù  
\v 16 A kamagh…®n me m…®kemegha, boriba vaghvagha me isa me musi. Egha dafarim vaghvagha me gis…®n ar…®ghava, God arazir aghuim me damuasa God…®n m…®gei. 
\s1 Bizir av…®riba itir gumazim 
\r (Matyu 19:16-30 ko Luk 18:18-30) 
\p  
\v 17 Egha Iesus d…®kavigha zuima, gumazir mam ivegha izava, uan tevimning ap…®righava Iesus…®n guam…®n kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisan Aghuim, k…® manmagh…®n damigh zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam?‚Äù  
\v 18 Ez…® Iesus a ikaragha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® manmagh sua gumazir aghuim na gar…®si? Gumazir aghuitam itir puvat…®. God uab…®ra gumazir aghuarim.  
\v 19 N…® God Moses gan…®ngizir arazim g…®fo, ‚ÄòN…® gumazim m…®sueght…® an aremeghan mark…®, n…® poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim damuam mark…®, n…® gumazir igharazim…®n biziba ok…®man mark…®, n…® bizibagh ifaran mark…®, n…® ua bagh biziba inis…® gumazibagh ifaran mark…®, n…® uan afeziam ko amebam…®n apengan ik…® aning…®n akaba baragh.‚Äô‚Äù  
\v 20 Ez…® an a ikaragha kamagh m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, k…® fom…®ram agh…®rimra ikiava arazir kabagh amua iza dat…®r…®gh…®n ikia kati.‚Äù  
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus gumazir kam…®n garava, a gifongegha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® bizir vam…®ra n…® t…®ghar a damuam. Bizir n…® itiba bar da amadagh…®va dag…®aba inigh, egh gumazir biziba puvat…®zibar an…®ngigh. Egh n…® God…®n Nguibam…®n bizir aghuariba iniam. Egh, nan g…®n iz…®.‚Äù  
\v 22 Ez…® gumazir kam akar kam baregha, an guam m…®s…®ngi. A fo, a guizbang…®ra bizir av…®riba itir gumazim. A kamagh…®n, an navim bar osemez…® a ghu. 
\p  
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus…®n damaziba uan suren gumazibagh aruava, kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir biziba av…®rasemeziba, me God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n mang…®s…® bar iburagham!‚Äù  
\v 24 An suren gumaziba an akar kaba baregha, d…®gavir kuram gamiz…®ma, Iesus ua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúBoriba, gumazim God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven mang…®s…®, a guizbang…®ra bar iburagham.  
\v 25 Kamel…®n tam iniba isair d…®konir torim…®n aven mang…®s…® ingangarir dafam damigh aven mangam. Eght…® gumazir biziba av…®rasemeziba, me God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven mang…®s…® guizbang…®ra bar iburagham!‚Äù\f + \ft (10:25) N…® kamel…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f* 
\v 26 A me m…®geima, me guizbang…®ra d…®gavir kuram gamuava n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amuava uarira uariv gei, ‚ÄúKamagh…®n damight…®ma, tinara zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuir kam iniam?‚Äù  
\v 27 Ez…® Iesus men garava kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúBizir kaba gumazim…®n bar osemegham. Bizir kaba God…®n osemezir puvat…®. A biziba bar dagh ami.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® Pita kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ge, e uan biziba bar da ategha, n…®n g…®n ize.‚Äù  
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, gumazitam nan akar aghuim ko na bagh, uan d…®penim, o uan aveghbuaba, o uan buaramiziba, o uan afeziam ko amebam, o uan boriba, o uan azeniba ategh,  
\v 30 egh gumazir kam dat…®r…®gh…®n nguazir kam…®n God guizbang…®ra bizir a faragha itiba bar dagh afiragh a dan…®ngam. A d…®penir av…®riba ko aveghbuaba ko buaramiziba ko amebaba ko borir av…®riba, ko azenir av…®riba a dan…®ngam. Eght…® God…®n g…®n zuir gumazibagh as…®ghas…®zir araziba a uaghan dar aven ikiam. Eght…®ma dughiar g…®n izamim zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim an a dan…®ngam.  
\v 31 Dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar kam…®n faragha itir gumazir av…®riba, me g…®n ik…®t…®ma, dat…®r…®gh…®n g…®n itir gumazir av…®riba, me g…®n faragh mangam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus uan ovevem, dughiar m…®kezim…®n uam a m…®gei. 
\r (Matyu 20:17-19 ko Luk 18:31-34) 
\p  
\v 32 Egha me Jerusalem…®n ghuavanagava Iesus faraz…®ma, an suren gumaziba an g…®n ghua n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amima, me ko zuir gumazamiziba atiati. Ez…® Iesus ua uan 12 plan suren gumaziba inigha me m…®riam…®n ghughava, a bativamin bizibar gun me m…®gei.  
\v 33 A kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa oragh. E nguibar ekiam Jerusalem…®n ghuavanadi. Eght…® gumazitam Gumazibar Otarim is…®va, Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba koma ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar an…®ngam. Eght…® me a is…® kot dat…®gh…®va, egh a m…®sueght…® an aremeghs…®va akabar ak…®ram, egh me kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m suam, An aremegham. Egh me a m…®sueght…® an aremeghs…®va, a inigh Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazibar dafaribar ar…®gham.  
\v 34 Egh Kantrin Igharazibar Gumaziba, me d…®bovir akabar a m…®k…®m…®va, a gipar…®va, a fozorogh…®va, egh a m…®sueght…® an aremegham. An aremeght…®, dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim g…®vaght…® a ua d…®kavigham.‚Äù 
\s1 Jems ko Jon ziar ekiamning iniasa ifonge. 
\r (Matyu 20:20-28) 
\p  
\v 35 Ez…® Sebedin otarimning, Jems ko Jon, Iesus bagha izava kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, ga bizir mam bagha ifonge. N…® ga bagha a damuasa ga n…®n azai.‚Äù  
\v 36 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n aning…®n azara, ‚ÄúK…® manmagh…®n guan akurvagham?‚Äù  
\v 37 Aning a ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® atrivir ekiam…®n otogh…®va egh ga damight…® gan tav n…®n agharir guvim daperaght…®, tav n…®n agharir k…®riam daperagham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 38 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua azangs…®zir bizir kam, gua an m…®ngarim g…®fozir puvat…®, egha ia a bagha nan azai. Gua ti k…® ateramin os…®mt…®zim, uaghan an ateramin gavgavim iti? O os…®mt…®zir d…®par k…® ruamim gua uaghan a guruam?‚Äù  
\v 39 Ez…® aning a ikara, ‚ÄúAre, ga gavgavim iti.‚Äù Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra, gua k…® ateramin os…®mt…®zim, gua a iniam, egh os…®mt…®zir d…®par k…® ruamim gua a guruam.  
\v 40 Egha gua nan agharir guvim ko k…®riam dapiasa azangs…®si, kar nan bizim puvat…®. Danganir kaba God…®n bizimra. A danganir kabar dapiamin gumaziba, a me g…®fogha, me bagha danganir kabagh ami.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 41 Ez…® Jems ko Jon bizir kam…®n Iesus m…®geima, 10 plan suren gumazir igharaziba a baregha, bizir kam bagha Jems ko Jon…®n atari.  
\v 42 Ez…® Iesus men diagha, me akuvagha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa fo, Kantrin Igharazibar atriviba pamten me gamima, me bar men apengan iti. Ez…® men gumazir dapaniba uan akaba baraghasa puv…®ra me ab…®raghb…®rasi.  
\v 43 Eght…® arazir kaba ian tong…®n ikian kogham. Gumazir manam ian tong…®n ekiam…®n ik…®s…®, a ingangarir gumazim…®n m…®n ik…®.  
\v 44 Eght…® gumazir manam ian faragh mang…®s…®, a bar ian ingangarir gumazir k…®nim…®n m…®n ik…®.  
\v 45 Ez…® kamagh…®ra Gumazibar Otarim iza, gumazamizibar amut…® me a bagh ingarasa, a izezir pu. Puvat…®, a me bagh ingarasa ize. A gumazamizir av…®riba bagh ovegh ua me givezegh me iniasa ize.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus gumazir damazir kurar mam gamiz…® a dera 
\r (Matyu 20:29-34 ko Luk 18:35-43) 
\p  
\v 46 Egha Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko Jerikon izegha, egha gumazamizir av…®rim sara nguibar ekiam ataghrasi. Ez…® gumazir damazir kurar mam, an ziam Bartimeus (Timeus…®n otarim), a tuavir m…®riam…®n aperaghav ikiava biziba bagha inge.  
\v 47 Egha an orazima Nasaret…®n gumazim Iesus uaghan iza zuima a dia ghaze, ‚ÄúIesus Devit…®n Otarim, nan apangkufigh!‚Äù  
\v 48 Ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba d…®man an anogoregha egha n…®m…®ra ikiasava a m…®gei. Ez…® a pamtem diav…®ra iti, ‚ÄúDevit…®n Otarim nan apangkufigh!‚Äù  
\v 49 Ez…® Iesus tugha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAn diagh.‚Äù Ez…® me gumazir damazir kuram…®n diagha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® uab…®n gavgafigh, egh d…®kafigh! Iesus n…®n dei.‚Äù  
\v 50 Ez…® a uan korotiar azenan azuim suegha anekunigha zuam…®ra d…®kavigha Iesus bagha ize.  
\v 51 Ez…® Iesus an azara, ‚ÄúK…® n…® bagh tizim damuasa n…® ifonge?‚Äù Ez…® gumazir damazir kuram kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, k…® ganasa ifonge.‚Äù  
\v 52 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúMang…®. N…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n itima, a n…® gamiz…® n…® ua dera.‚Äù Ez…® zuam…®ra a ua gari. Egha a Iesus…®n g…®n tuavim…®n zui. 
\c 11  
\ms1 Iesus m…®zazim inigha aremegha ua d…®kafi 
\mr (Sapta 11-16) 
\s1 Iesus atrivim…®n m…®n Jerusalem…®n zui 
\r (Matyu 21:1-11 ko Luk 19:28-40 ko Jon 12:12-19) 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko Jerusalem…®n borogh…®n izava Betfage ko Betanin borogh…®n Oliv…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n oto. Egha Iesus uan suren gumazir pumuning aning amaga,  
\v 2 kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua nguibar munagh itim…®n mang…®, gua an mang…®va gant…®ma donkin igiar mam, me a ikez…®ma, a iti. Gumazitam dughiatam…®n a gaperaghava aruizir puvat…®. Gua an benim f…®righ…®va a inigh kagh iz…®.\f + \ft (11:2) N…® donkin m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f* 
\v 3 Eght…® tav guan azang suam, ‚ÄòGua tizim bagha donki f…®ri?‚Äô gua kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòEkiam ingangarim an iti. A uam anemangam.‚Äô‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® aning ghua garima, me donki d…®penir tiar akam…®n azenan tuavim…®n a ike. Ez…® aning a f…®rima,  
\v 5 gumazir maba tuivighav ikia aning…®n azara, ‚ÄúGua tizim bagha donkin benim f…®ri?‚Äù  
\v 6 Ez…® Iesus aning m…®kemez…® moghon aning men akam ikara. Ez…® gumaziba aning…®n amamangat…®z…®ma aning zui.  
\v 7 Egha aning donki inigha Iesus bagha izeghava uan korotiar azenan azuiba suegha donki gis…®n da ghuani. Ez…® Iesus a gis…®n apera.  
\v 8 Ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba uan korotiar azenan azuiba suegha tuavim…®n da ghuari. Ez…® marazi ruarim…®n tev seviba aghoregha da ar…®si.  
\v 9 Egha faragha zuiba ko g…®n zuiba me diava ara kamagh…®n m…®gei, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúHosana! Ia God…®n ziam f…®! 
\q2 Gumazir kam Ekiam…®n ziam ko gavgavim…®n izi. 
\q3 God derav…®ra a damu.‚Äù 
\q1  
\v 10 ‚ÄúEn ovavim Devit fom…®ra en atrivim…®n ikez…® mogh…®n 
\q3 gumazir kam en atrivim…®n ikiasa izi. 
\q2 Eght…® God derav…®ra a damu. 
\q3 Hosana! Biziba bar dar p…®n itir God…®n ziam f…®!‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Iesus Jerusalem…®n aven ghugha ghua God…®n D…®penir m…®riam…®n ghu. A ghugha biziba dar garava da asavsuisi. Ez…® aruem g…®vaz…® a suren gumaziba ko me Betanin ghue. 
\s1 Iesus temer figh bar an anogoroke 
\r (Matyu 21:18-19) 
\p  
\v 12 Am…®m…®zaraghan Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko ua Betani ataghragha, Iesus m…®tiriam an azi.  
\v 13 A saghon garima temer figh…®n mam dafaribara iti. Ez…® a rogh…®ra mang…® foghasa a dagheba iti, o puvat…®. Kar figh…®n temeba bamin dughiam puvat…®. Ez…® kamagh…®n a ghua ov…®zitam…®n apizir puvat…®, dafarir k…®nbaram an iti.\f + \ft (11:13) N…® figh…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f* 
\v 14 Egha a kamagh…®n temem m…®gei, ‚ÄúTav g…®n n…®n ov…®zitam rameghan kogham.‚Äù An a m…®kemez…®, an suren gumaziba oraki. 
\s1 Iesus God…®n D…®penir m…®riam…®n ghua gumazir as…®ziba amadiba me batosi 
\r (Matyu 21:12-17 ko Luk 19:45-48 ko Jon 2:13-22) 
\p  
\v 15 Egha Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko Jerusalem…®n otivigha, Iesus God…®n D…®penir m…®riam…®n ghuava gumazir as…®zir ofa gamibagh iveziba ko as…®zir ofa gamiba amadiba me batosi. Egha dag…®aba uari ikarvazir gumazibar dakoziba ko kuarazir bunbaba amadibar dabirabiba, da fava egha da ighaghar…®si.  
\v 16 Egha a tav bizir amaditam inigh God…®n D…®penir m…®riam…®n aven iz…® mangan an anogoroke.  
\v 17 Egha a men sure gamuava kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúM…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n osizirim…®n iti, o puvat…®? 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄòNan d…®penim…®n ingangarim…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, 
\q2 kar nguaziba bar men Gumazamiziba 
\q3 God ko M…®geir D…®penim.‚Äô 
\b  
\m Ez…® ia gumazir okeibar danganir mogomem…®n m…®n a gami.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Gumazamizir av…®rim bar an suren m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baregha d…®gavir kuram gami. Ez…® kamagh…®n ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba Iesus…®n atiatigha, egh me a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa magh…®ra tuaviba buri.  
\v 19 Ez…® aruem gevima Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko me Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam ategha azenan zui. 
\s1 Temer figh…®n m…®s…®ngizim 
\r (Matyu 21:20-22) 
\p  
\v 20 Egha m…®zaraghara Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko ghua garima temer figh…®n biba sara m…®s…®ngi.  
\v 21 Ez…® Pita n…®r…®gha Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa n…® gan, temer figh…®n n…® as…®ghas…®ghasa m…®kemezim, a m…®s…®ngi!‚Äù  
\v 22 Iesus an m…®g…®r…®g…®am ikaragha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ik…®.  
\v 23 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, tina m…®ghs…®ar kam m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòMang…® uab…® fegh ongarim m…®k…®nigh,‚Äô egh uan navir averiam…®n igharagh n…®ghn…®ghan kogh, egh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim a m…®kemezir bizim…®n ik…® suam, ‚ÄòAn otivam,‚Äô eght…® bizir kam a bagh otogham.  
\v 24 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma k…® ia m…®gei, ia bizir tizim bagh God ko m…®geir dughiam an azangs…®gh, egh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…® suam, ‚ÄòK…® a inigha g…®fa,‚Äô n…® bizir kam inigham.  
\v 25-26 Egh n…® tugh God ko m…®k…®m…®va egh os…®mt…®zim tinan iti, n…® an arazir kuram g…®n amadagh, eght…® kamagh…®n n…®n Afeziar Ekiar uan nguibam…®n itim n…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham.‚Äù\f + \ft (11:26) Fofozir gumazir maba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir mam uaghan vez…®n kam…®n aven iti. M…®g…®r…®g…®ar kamra kara, ‚ÄúEgh ia gumazamizir igharaziba, ia gamizir arazir kuraba g…®n amadaghan koght…®, ian Afeziar uan nguibam…®n itim a uaghan ian arazir kuraba g…®n amadaghan kogham.‚Äù\f* 
\s1 Judan gumazir dapaniba Iesus…®n gavgavim bagha azara 
\r (Matyu 21:23-27 ko Luk 20:1-8) 
\p  
\v 27 Egha Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko uamategha Jerusalem…®n otogha Iesus God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®riam…®n aven aruima, ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Judan gumazir dapaniba a bagha ize.  
\v 28 Egha Iesus…®n azara, ‚ÄúN…® gavgavir manam…®n amodogh…®n bizir kabagh ami? Egha tina bizir kabar amuasa gavgavim n…® gan…®ngi?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus me ikara, ‚ÄúK…® azangs…®zir mam ia damuasa ia na m…®kemeght…® k…® gavgavir manam…®n bizir kabagha amim…®n gun ia m…®k…®mam.  
\v 30 Jon…®n rurim‚Äîkar God…®n bizim, o gumazibar bizim? Na m…®kemegh!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 31 Ez…® me uarira uariv kemegha ghaze, ‚ÄúE suam, ‚ÄòAn rurim God…®n ize,‚Äô eght…®ma a kamagh…®n ua en azaragham, ‚ÄòIa manmagh…®n amigha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Jon damuan aghua?‚Äô  
\v 32 Eght…® e suam, ‚ÄòAn rurim gumazibar ize‚Äô....‚Äù (Gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra fo, Jon a guizbang…®ra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, kamagh…®n me gumazamizibar atiatingi.)  
\v 33 Egha me Iesus…®n azangs…®zim ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE fozir puvat…®.‚Äù Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKamagh…®ra, k…® uan gavgavim inizir tuavim…®n, gun ia m…®kemeghan kogham.‚Äù 
\c 12  
\s1 Wain…®n azenim…®n garir gumazir kurabar akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Matyu 21:33-46 ko Luk 20:9-19) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus akar is…®n zuibar Judan gumazir dapanibav gei, ‚ÄúGumazir mam wain…®n azenim oparigha an d…®vazim aghui. Egha wain…®n ov…®ziba m…®rm…®ramin itarim gukuigha p…®n ik…® wain…®n azenim…®n ganamin d…®penim…®n ingari. Egha a wain…®n azenim isa wain…®n azenim…®n ganamin gumazir mabagh an…®ngi (eght…® me g…®n wain taba uam a ikaragham). Egha saghon igharagha ghu.\f + \ft (12:1) N…® wain…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f* 
\v 2 Ez…® wain…®n ov…®ziba kuaramin dughiam otoz…®, wain…®n azenir ghuavim ingangarir gumazir mam amadaz…® a wain…®n ov…®zir taba iniasa wain…®n azenim…®n garir gumaziba bagha ghu.  
\v 3 Ez…® me an suiragha, a m…®suegha anemadaz…® a dafaribara uamatenge.  
\v 4 Ez…® a ingangarir gumazir igharazim amadaz…® me a m…®sogha an dapanim abigha aghums…®zir arazibar a gami.  
\v 5 Ez…® a ua m…®kezim amada, ez…® kam me a m…®soghez…® an areme. Ez…® an av…®rir igharazir maba saram amangi; maba me pura me m…®soke, maba me me m…®soghez…® me ariagh…®re. 
\p  
\v 6 ‚ÄúEz…® bar abuananam iti anenemangasa, an otarir kamra, a bar ifongezim. A bar men g…®n anemagava kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòMe nan otarir kam…®n akam baregh deragh a damuam.‚Äô Egha anemadaz…® a ghu.  
\v 7 Ez…® wain…®n azenim…®n garir gumaziba kamagh…®n uariv gei, ‚ÄòKar g…®n wain…®n azenir kam iniamin otarim. Aria, e uari inigh a m…®sueght…® an aremeka. Egh wain…®n azenir kam, e an ghuaviba ikegham.‚Äô  
\v 8 Egha me an suiragha a m…®soghez…® an areme. Ez…® me a isava wain…®n azenim…®n azenan anekuni. 
\p  
\v 9 ‚ÄúEz…® wain…®n azenim…®n ghuavim bar manmagh…®ra damuam? A iz…®va wain…®n azenim…®n garir gumazir kabav soght…®ma me ar…®m…®ghiram. Egh wain…®n azenim is…®va igharaz darazir aningam.  
\v 10-11 Ia God…®n Ak…®nafarir osizirir kam…®n ganiz, o puvat…®? 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄòKar d…®penir ak…®nir ingangarir gumaziba aghuazim, 
\q2 a dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®penim aterir guarim gava. 
\q1 Kar Ekiam arazir kam gami, 
\q2 ez…® an en ganganim…®n 
\q3 bar dera.‚Äô‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® me fo an akar is…®n zuim me gasara, ez…® kamagh…®n me an suiragh a iniasa tuaviba buri. Egha me an suighasa gumazamizibar atiatigha, anetegha ghue. 
\s1 Gumazamiziba dag…®aba Sisar dan…®ngam, o puvat…®gham? 
\r (Matyu 22:15-22 ko Luk 20:20-26) 
\p  
\v 13 Egha g…®n Judan gumazir dapaniba Farisin maba ko Herot…®n g…®n zuir darasi amadaz…®, me Iesus bagha ize. Eght…® me Iesus…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevitam…®n an suighasa.  
\v 14 Me izegha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, e fo, n…® zurara guizbang…®ra m…®g…®ava, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar vam…®ra gumazamiziba bar me gan…®di. Gumazir ziaba itiba o gumazir k…®niba, n…® akar vam…®ra me m…®g…®ava guizbang…®ra God…®n arazibar men sure gami. E God…®n arazim g…®n mang…®va, gavman…®n dag…®aba Sisar dan…®ngam o puvat…®gham? E ivezam, o ivezan kogham?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Iesus men ifavarim g…®fogha kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha na gifari? Dag…®atam na bagh a inigh iz…®t…® k…® an ganika.‚Äù  
\v 16 Ez…® me dag…®am a bagha a inigha izez…® a men azara, ‚ÄúTinan nedazim ko ziamra kara?‚Äù Ez…® me kamagh…®n Iesus ikara, ‚ÄúSisar…®n nedazim.‚Äù  
\v 17 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúKamagh…®ra, ia Sisar…®n biziba Sisar dan…®ng…®va, God…®n biziba is…®, God dan…®ng.‚Äù Ez…® me an ikarvazim…®n d…®gavir kuram gami. 
\s1 Sadyusiba gumazim aremegh ua d…®kavamin bizim bagha Iesus…®n azangs…®si 
\r (Matyu 22:23-33 ko Luk 20:27-40) 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® Sadyusiba, me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, gumazim aremegh ua d…®kavighan kogham. Egha me azangs…®zir mam sara Iesus bagha ize.\f + \ft (12:18) N…® Sadyusibar m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f* 
\v 19 Me izegha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, Moses fom…®ra kamagh…®n e bagha osiri, gumazim ovegh uan amuim ategh egh boriba puvat…®ght…®, an aveghbuam an amuir odiarim…®n ik…®va a bagh boriba iniam.  
\v 20-21 Ez…® dughiar mam 7 pla aveghbuaba iti. Avebam amuim…®n ikia boriba puvat…®gha aremez…®ma, ua avebamra irim an ikia boriba puvat…®ghava uaghan areme. Ez…® m…®kezim kamagh…®ram ami.  
\v 22 Ez…® 7 pla aveghbuar kaba bar me an ikia, boritaba inizir puvat…®gha ariagh…®re. Ez…® abuan, amizim uaghan areme.  
\v 23 Aveghbuar 7 pla an ike. Egh kamagh…®n ua d…®kavamin dughiam, tinarama an pam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me ikara, ‚ÄúIa God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n osizirim ko God…®n gavgavim g…®fozir puvat…®, kamagh…®n ia paza n…®ghn…®gha m…®gei?  
\v 25 Ariaghreziba d…®kavamin dughiam paba amuibar ikian kogham, uaghan me amuiba is…® pabar ar…®ghan kogham. Me enselbar m…®n God…®n Nguibam…®n ikiam. 
\p  
\v 26 ‚ÄúEz…® ariaghreziba ua d…®kavizir bizim bagha, ia Moses…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n aven temer isizim…®n eghaghanim ia an gani, o puvat…®? Eghaghanir kam…®n, God kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme, ‚ÄòK…® Abraham, ko Aisak ko Jekop…®n God.‚Äô  
\v 27 God gumazibar nivaf…®zir ariagh…®ribar God puvat…®, a gumazibar duar angamra itibar God. Ia bar paza n…®ghn…®gha m…®gei.‚Äù 
\s1 God…®n arazir faragha zuim 
\r (Matyu 22:34-40 ko Luk 10:25-28) 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® Judan arazibagh fozir gumazir mam izima Sadyusiba Iesus ko uari adozima, a me barasi. An orazima Iesus ikarvazir aghuim me gan…®ngiz…®ma, a Iesus…®n azara, ‚ÄúGod…®n arazir manamra maba bar dagh afiragha, faragha zui?‚Äù  
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus a ikara, ‚ÄúArazir bar ekiamra kara: ‚ÄòIsrael, ia oragh. Ekiam en God, Ekiam uab…®ra.  
\v 30 Ia uan Ekiam, ian God, uan navir averiam ko uan duam ko uan n…®ghn…®zim ko uan gavgavim sara bar a gifongegh.‚Äô  
\v 31 Ez…® arazir anar…®ra irimra kara, ‚ÄòN…® uab…® gifongezir mogh…®n gumazamiziba bar me gifongegh.‚Äô Ua arazitam kamning…®n m…®n ekevegha aning gafirazir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 32 Ez…® gumazir kam kamagh…®n Iesus ikara, ‚ÄúN…® guizbang…®ra m…®g…®a ghaze, God uab…®ra, tav ua itir puvat…®.  
\v 33 E uan navir averiam ko, uan n…®ghn…®zim ko uan gavgavim…®n Ekiam gifongegh, egh uab…® gifongezir mogh…®n gumazamiziba bar me gifongegham. E arazir kamning…®n g…®n mangam, eght…® arazir kamning ofan me bar avim…®n tueba ko ofa damuamin biziba bar dagh afira.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 34 Iesus orazima a derav…®ra m…®kemez…®, Iesus a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® God biziba bar dagh ativagh dar ganamin dughiam…®n saghon itir puvat…®.‚Äù Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n tav ua azangs…®zitam ua Iesus damuan atiatingi. 
\s1 Iesus, God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim bagha gumazamizibar azangs…®si 
\r (Matyu 22:41-46; 23:1-36 ko Luk 11:37-54; Luk 20:41-47) 
\p  
\v 35 Egha Iesus God…®n D…®penir m…®riam…®n gumazamizibar sure gamuava, men azara, ‚ÄúManmagh amiz…® Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Krais, God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, a Devit…®n ovavim?  
\v 36 Devit uab…®, God…®n Duam n…®ghn…®zir kam a gan…®ngiz…®, a kamagh…®n m…®keme, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄòEkiam, nan Ekiam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, 
\q2 ‚ÄúNan agharir guvim daperagh, 
\q3 egh na ko atrivim…®n ikiam. 
\q1 Egh mang…® dughiar k…® n…®n apanibar amight…® 
\q2 me n…®n apengan ikiam.‚Äù ‚Äô 
\b  
\m  
\v 37 Egha Devit uab…® ‚ÄòEkiam‚Äô gumazir kam gat…®. Ez…® manmagh…®n amiz…® a ua Devit…®n Otarim?‚Äù Ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baregha bar akonge. 
\p  
\v 38 Ez…® Iesus gumazamizibar sure gamua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba bagh ganigh. Me korotiar ruaribar aghuigh darut…® gumazamiziba me biziba amaga dagh ivezi nagh…®n ziar ekiaba me dan…®ngasa, me bar ifonge.  
\v 39 Egh God ko m…®geir d…®penibar dabirabir aghuariba iniva, egh isar ekiabar dughiaba me danganir ziaba itiba iniasa bar ifonge.  
\v 40 Me amuir odiaribagh ifarava men d…®peniba ok…®a, ghaze e dera. Egha gumaziba men ziaba fasa, egha me God ko m…®g…®a m…®g…®r…®g…®ar ruaribagh ami. Kamagh…®n amir gumaziba, men ivezir kuram gumazir arazir kurabagh amibar ivezim bar a gafiragham.‚Äù 
\s1 Amuir odiarim…®n ofa 
\r (Luk 21:1-4) 
\p  
\v 41 Egha Iesus ghua dag…®aba ar…®zir danganim…®n borogh…®n aperaghav ikiava gumazamizir av…®ribar garima me uan dag…®aba isa God…®n D…®penim…®n dag…®aba ar…®zir danganim…®n a da ar…®si. Gumazamizir dag…®ar av…®riba itiba dag…®ar av…®riba ar…®si.  
\v 42 Ez…® biziba puvat…®zir amuir odiarim izava dag…®ar muziarir pumuning at…®, aning dag…®ar rubuzir muziarir vam…®ra an m…®n ghu.  
\v 43 Ez…® Iesus uan suren gumazibar diagha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, biziba puvat…®zir amuir odiarir kam dag…®ar muziarir pumuning dag…®aba ar…®zir danganim gat…®, ez…® an dag…®ar pumuning gumazir igharaziba ar…®gh…®zir dag…®abagh afira.  
\v 44 Me uan dag…®ar av…®ribar amodogh…®n dag…®ar muziariba an…®ngi. Ez…®ma a uan dabirabir onganarazim…®n m…®rara dag…®ar muziarir abuananam at…®.‚Äù 
\c 13  
\s1 Iesus ghaze, God…®n D…®penim g…®n ikuvigham 
\r (Matyu 24:1-2 ko Luk 21:5-6) 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Iesus God…®n D…®penim ategha azenan zuima, an suren gumazir mam a m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa! N…® gan, kar dag…®ar bar ekiaba, me dar God…®n D…®penim…®n ingariz…®ma, an ganganim bar dera! God…®n D…®penim koma d…®penir dozir an m…®riam…®n itiba, da bar d…®penir diriba!‚Äù  
\v 2 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a ikara, ‚ÄúN…® d…®penir dafar kabanagh…®n gari? Da bar ikuvigham. Egh dag…®ar kaba, gumaziba bar da pueght…® da bar mogh…®ra dagh iregham. Eght…® tam tam gis…®n ikeghan kogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, os…®mt…®zir av…®riba g…®n otivam 
\r (Matyu 24:3-14 ko Luk 21:7-19) 
\p  
\v 3 Egha Iesus Oliv…®n m…®ghs…®am gis…®n, God…®n D…®penim…®n guam a m…®suegha aperaghav itima, Pita, Jems, Jon ko Andru me uarira ikiava an azara,  
\v 4 ‚ÄúE m…®kemegh, d…®peniba ikuvighamin bizim, a manad…®zogh…®n otivam? Eght…® arazir manam faragh otoght…®ma, e fogh suam bizir kaba otivamin dughiam rogh…®ra ize?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uari bagh deraghv…®ra gan, gumazitam iz…® ia gifaran mark…®.  
\v 6 Gumazir av…®riba nan ziam…®n iz…®, suam, ‚ÄòK…® Krais, God ua e iniasa m…®sevezir gumazim,‚Äô egh gumazamizir av…®ribagh ifaram. 
\p  
\v 7 ‚ÄúEght…® ia rogh…®ra itir m…®dorozir ekiabar n…®g…®niba baragh, egh saghon itir m…®dorozir ekiabar akaba baragham. Egh ia d…®gavir kuram damuan mark…®. Arazir kaba otivam, eght…® nguazir kam g…®vamin dughiam t…®ghar izam.  
\v 8 Kantrin mam…®n itir darazi d…®kavigh kantrin igharazim…®n itir darazi ko m…®sogham. Eght…® atrivir mam…®n adarazi d…®kavigh atrivir igharazim…®n adarazi ko m…®sogham. Danganir mabar dagheba bar puvat…®ght…®ma, gumazamiziba m…®tiriamra ikiam. Eght…®ma m…®k…®mk…®ziba uaghan otivam. Os…®mt…®zir kaba faragh otivight…® nguazir kam g…®vamin dughiam t…®ghar. Os…®mt…®zir kaba mati, amizim otasa faraghav…®ra m…®zazim isi mok…®n. 
\p  
\v 9 ‚ÄúIa derav…®ra uari bagh gan. Gumazitaba ia is…® nguibabar garir gumazibar an…®ngam. Egh me God ko m…®geir d…®penibar ia m…®sogham. Egh ia na bang…®n atriviba ko gavman…®n gumazir ekiabar damazibar tuiva, egh ka amizir biziba ia dar gun me m…®k…®mam.  
\v 10 Eght…® God…®n akar aghuim gumaziba faragh nguibaba bar dav k…®nigh.  
\v 11 Eght…® gumazitaba dughiar manam ian suiragh ia inigh kot…®n mang…®t…®, ia faragh m…®k…®ms…® n…®ghn…®gh…®va os…®man mark…®. Pura m…®g…®r…®g…®ar manam God kot…®n aven n…® danight…®, na m…®k…®m. Kar n…® uab…® m…®geir puvat…®, God…®n Duam m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 12 ‚ÄúAveghbuaba uarira uari is…® apanibar an…®ngt…® me me m…®soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiram. Eght…® afeziaba uan boriba uaghan kamagh…®ra dar amuam. Boriba uan ameboghfeziabar akaba batogh…®va ovengamin arazibar me damut…®, me ar…®m…®ghiram.  
\v 13 Eght…® gumazamiziba bar nan ziam bang…®n ian aghuagham. Egh tina tugh gavgavigh mang…® ana aremeghamin dughiam…®n tught…®, God ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim g…®n a dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, bizir bar kuram otivam 
\r (Matyu 24:15-28 ko Luk 21:20-24) 
\p  
\v 14 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gant…® God bar aghuazir bizim an d…®penim…®n ikiam. Kar a ikian koghamin danganim. A ik…®t…®, God uan D…®penim ategham. (N…® tina osizirir kam…®n ganigh, derav…®ra n…®ghn…®gh…®va a g…®fogh.) God bar aghuazir bizir kam, dughiar kam…®n otoght…®, Judian Distrigh…®n aven itir darasi me zuam…®ram ar…® m…®ghs…®abar ghuavanangam.  
\v 15 Tav d…®penim…®n avughsir danganim…®n ikegh…®va d…®penim…®n aven mang…® uan bizitam inian mark…®.  
\v 16 Tav azenir ekiam…®n ikegh…®va uamategh d…®penim…®n mang…® uan azenan azuir korotiam inian mark…®.  
\v 17 Naviba adair amiziba ko boriba oteba apir amebaba, mevzika; dughiar izamin kaba bar men ikuvigham!  
\v 18-19 Dughiar izamin kaba, da os…®mt…®zir ekiabar dughiaba. God nguazim ko overiam…®n ingarizir dughiam…®n iza dat…®r…®k…®n, egh ua kamagh…®n dughiatam otoghan kogham. Ez…® kamagh…®n ia God ko m…®k…®m, eght…® os…®mt…®zir ekiar kaba amozim…®n dughiam…®n otivan mark…®.  
\v 20 Egha Ekiam uan m…®sevezir gumazamizibagh n…®ghn…®gha, dughiar kurar kam…®n dughiar maba aghorez…® da mong otefe. A ti dar aghorezir puvat…®z…® gumazamiziba bar ariaghreghai. 
\p  
\v 21 ‚ÄúDughiar izamim tav ia m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIa gan, Kraisra kara! A God Ua E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazimra,‚Äô o, ‚ÄòIa gan, Kraisra muna!‚Äô an akam baraghan mark…®.  
\v 22 Gumazitaba iz…®va ia gifar suam, ‚ÄòK…®rara, God Gumazamiziba Ua Me Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim,‚Äô o ‚Äòk…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam,‚Äô egh me mirakel…®n bar ekiaba koma d…®gavir kuram gamir arazibar amut…® da otivam. Me kamagh…®n ifonge, me gumazamizibagh ifaraght…®, me onganigham. Egh me gavgavim ik…®, uaghan God ua bagha m…®sevezir gumazamiziba, me uaghan me gifarasa. Kamagh…®n me mirakel…®n kabar amuam. Egh dughiataba me me gifars…® damuva avegham.  
\v 23 K…® g…®n otivamin biziba bar dar gun ia m…®keme. Kamagh…®n ia derav…®ra uari bagh gan.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, g…®n Gumazibar Otarim izam 
\r (Matyu 24:29-31 ko Luk 21:25-28) 
\p  
\v 24 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúOs…®mt…®zir ekiar kabar dughiam g…®vaght…®, g…®n izamin dughiam…®n bizir kaba otivam. 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄòAruem m…®tategham, 
\q2 eght…® iakinim isiraghan kogham; 
\q1  
\v 25 eght…® m…®koveziba overiam…®n asigh…®ram, 
\q2 eght…® overiam…®n itir bizir gavgaviba s…®vaghs…®vagh, 
\q3 uan danganiba ataghragham.‚Äô 
\b  
\m  
\v 26 Dughiar kam…®n gumaziba gant…® Gumazibar Otarim gavgavir ekiam ko angazangarir ekiam sara ghuariam…®n tong…®n izam.  
\v 27 Egh a uan enselba amadaght…® me mang…® nguazim ko overiam…®n danganiba bar ko nguazim…®n oteviba bar dar mang…®va God m…®sevezir gumazamiziba men aku a bagh izam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, ia temer figh…®n gan fogh 
\r (Matyu 24:32-35 ko Luk 21:29-33) 
\p  
\v 28 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTemer figh…®n aguaba ua d…®z murt…®, ia fogh suam, amozim…®n dughiam rogh…®ra ize. Ia temer figh…®n gan n…®ghn…®zim iniam.  
\v 29 Kamagh…®ra ia bizir kabar gant…® da otivt…®, ia fogh suam, Gumazibar Otarim a ua izamin dughiam rogh…®ra ize. A tiar akam…®n tughav iti.  
\v 30 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei dughiar kam…®n itir gumazamizir kaba ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…® bizir kaba bar otivam.  
\v 31 Overiam ko nguazim g…®vagham, eght…® nan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba g…®vaghan kogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, a ua izamin dughiam tav a g…®fozir puvat…® 
\r (Matyu 24:36-44) 
\p  
\v 32 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTav fozir puvat…®, dughiar manamra k…® ia m…®geir bizir kaba otivam. God…®n Nguibam…®n itir enselba ko God…®n Otarim uaghan fozir puvat…®. Afeziar Ekiam uab…®ra fo. 
\p  
\v 33 ‚ÄúIa dughiar kam…®n izamin dughiam g…®fozir puvat…®. Ia derav…®ra uari bagh gan…®va m…®zuam.  
\v 34 Dughiar kam mati gumazim igharagha zui. A uan d…®penim ategha ghua uan d…®penim isa uan ingangarir gumazibar dafarim garighava d…®penim…®n ingangariba me rome. A tiar akam…®n itir gumazim…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® derav…®ra gan. 
\p  
\v 35 ‚ÄúD…®penim…®n ghuavim izamin dughiam ia a g…®fozir puvat…®, a bogarangra izam, o d…®magarir ar…®zim…®n izam, o tuariba ak…®t…® a izam, o am…®nim tiraght…® a izam, o? Kamagh…®n ia derav…®ra gan.  
\v 36 Puvat…®ght…®ma, a zuam…®ram otogh ian gant…®, ia dakuv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 37 K…® ia m…®geir bizir kaba, k…® gumazamiziba bar me m…®gei, ‚ÄòIa derav…®ra gan!‚Äô‚Äù 
\c 14  
\s1 Gumazir dapaniba Iesus m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa m…®g…®r…®g…®abar k…®ri 
\r (Matyu 26:1-5 ko Luk 22:1-2 ko Jon 11:45-53) 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar kam, God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam, koma Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam, dughiar pumuningra ikiav…®ra itima, ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, koma Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba, arazir mogometam…®n Iesus…®n suiragh am…®sueght…® an aremeghasa tuaviba buri.\f + \ft (14:1) N…® Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam koma Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam…®n m…®ngariba g…®foghs…®, n…® ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f* 
\v 2 Me kamagh…®n uariv gei, ‚ÄúE isam…®n dughiam…®n an suighan kogham. E damut…® isam…®n itir gumazamiziba m…®dorozir ekiatam e damigham.‚Äù 
\s1 Amizir mam mughuriar aghuim zuir borem Iesus…®n dapanim ginge. 
\r (Matyu 26:6-13 ko Jon 12:1-8) 
\p  
\v 3 Egha Iesus Betanin nguibam…®n ikiava lepa itir gumazim Saimon…®n d…®penim…®n aven dagher dakozim…®n apava aperaghav iti. An apava aperaghav itima, amizir mam mughuriar aghuim zuir borer mam. An alabastan ingarizir m…®sevim…®n iti. An ziam nat, an ivezim bar p…®n iti. Amizir kam borer kam inigha Iesus bagha izegha borev sevim abigha borem Iesus…®n dapanim ginge.  
\v 4 Ez…® uaghan itir darasi me naviba isiava kamagh…®n uariv g…®av…®ra iti, ‚ÄúTizim bagha kav borer mughuriar aghuim zuim pazava a gami?  
\v 5 An anemadagha dag…®ar av…®riba inighai. An ivezim azenir vam…®ran ivezim gafira. Eght…® an dag…®aba onganarazibagh amibar akuragham.‚Äù Egha me puv an atari, egha an anogorosi.  
\v 6 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAnetakigh. Ia tizim bagha os…®mt…®zim a gar…®si? Anetakigh! An arazir aghuim na gami.  
\v 7 Onganarazibagh amiba zurara ia ko ikiam. Ia dughiar manam men akurvaghs…®, men akurvagh. K…® zurara ia ko ikian kogham.  
\v 8 K…® aremeght…® a damuamin bizim, a na gami. A faragh mughuriar aghuim zuir borem nan m…®karzim daghuight…® me g…®n na mozim dar…®gham.  
\v 9 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, me nguazir kam…®n danganir manam…®n God…®n akar aghuim akun…®va egh amizir kam amizir arazim uaghan a m…®k…®m…®va egh a g…®n…®ghn…®gh…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\s1 Judas Iskariot Iesus inigh ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar dafarim dar…®ghasa akar gavgavim ark…®ri 
\r (Matyu 26:14-16 ko Luk 22:3-6) 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Judas Iskariot 12 plan aposel…®n mam, a Iesus is…®va ofa gamir gumazir ekiabar dafarim dar…®ghasa me bagha ghu.  
\v 11 Ez…® me an akar kam baregha bar akonge, egha dag…®aba a dan…®ngasa akar gavgavim ark…®ri. Ez…® an an suiragh me dan…®ngasa tuaviba buri. 
\s1 Iesus uan suren gumaziba koma api 
\r (Matyu 26:17-25 ko Luk 22:7-14 ko 22:21-23 ko Jon 13:21-30) 
\p  
\v 12 Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiabar faragha zuir dughiam, Judan gumaziba me arazir kam iti. Me faragh God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam g…®n…®ghn…®gh…®va sipsip…®n igiam inigh God danigh…®va an ofa damuam. Ez…® Iesus…®n suren gumaziba an azara, ‚ÄúN…® danganir manam…®n, e mang…®, n…® God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam…®n isam ram…®s…®, e bizibar ak…®ram?‚Äù  
\v 13 Ez…® a uan suren gumazir pumuning amaga kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua nguibar ekiam…®n mang…®t…® gumazitam d…®par m…®nem ater iz…® gua batoght…®, gua an g…®n mang…®.  
\v 14 D…®penir an aven zuim gua an mang…®va an ghuavim m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòTisa kamagh…®n azangs…®si, ‚ÄúNan danganir k…® uan suren gumaziba ko Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam…®n isamar amamim mana?‚Äù ‚Äô  
\v 15 Eght…® a d…®penim…®n aven p…®n itir danganir ekiam ian akagham. Danganir kam biziba bar ikia e baghav…®ra m…®zuai. Eght…® ia danganir kam e uari bagh biziba bar dar ak…®r.‚Äù  
\v 16 Ez…® an suren gumazimning me ategha nguibar ekiam…®n aven ghua garima biziba a m…®g…®r…®g…®am…®n m…®rara ghuz…®, ez…® aning magh…®ra God Israelbagh Itazir Dughiam bagha dagheba ko bizibar k…®ri. 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® guarat…®zim…®n Iesus uan 12 plan suren gumaziba ko otifi.  
\v 18 Egha me dagher dakozim…®n apiaghav ikiava apava, Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ian tav na is…®va gumazir nan apanim gamibar agharim dar…®gham, a uaghan na ko ikiava api.‚Äù  
\v 19 Me an akam baregha, naviba bar oseme. Egha me bar vaghvagha an azangs…®gha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…®rara markiama?‚Äù  
\v 20 Ez…® a me ikaragha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa 12 pla ian tavra. Gumazir na ko itarir vam…®ra bret azuim.  
\v 21 Ez…® Gumazibar Otarim, God…®n Akinafarim m…®kemezir mogh…®n, an aremegham. Eght…® gumazir Gumazibar Otarim isava apanibar agharim gat…®zim, gumaka! A bar ikuvigham! Amebam a batezir puvat…®z…®, deraghai!‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus bret ko wain uan suren gumazibagh an…®ngi 
\r (Matyu 26:26-30 ko Luk 22:15-20 ko 1 Korin 11:23-25) 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko apa ikiava, a bret…®n mam inigha God m…®nabagha egha anebigha, a isa uan suren gumazibagh an…®ngi. Egha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar nan nivaf…®zim. Ia a inigh anerem…®.‚Äù  
\v 23 Egha a wain apir itarim inigha egha God m…®nabagha me gan…®ngiz…®, ez…® me vaghvagha uarir guri.  
\v 24 Me wain apima a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar nan ghuzim, an Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim, a gavgavim a gan…®di. A gumazamizir av…®riba bagha ire.  
\v 25 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, K…® uam wain…®n ov…®zim…®n d…®patam rameghan kogham, kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® Dughiar God Bizibagh Ativamim…®n otogham. Eght…® dughiar kam, k…® wain…®n d…®par igiam ramam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 26 Egha me God…®n ziam fer ighiar mam gamigha d…®kavigha Oliv…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n ghue. 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, Pita g…®n m…®k…®m suam, a Iesus g…®fozir puvat…®. 
\r (Matyu 26:31-35 ko Luk 22:31-34 ko Jon 13:36-38) 
\p  
\v 27 Egha Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúGod…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n osizirim kamagh…®n iti, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄòK…® sipsipbar garir gumazim a m…®sueght…® 
\q2 sipsipba tintinim…®n aregham.‚Äô 
\b  
\m Kamagh…®n ia bar n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itim g…®vaght…®ma, ia na ategh aregham.  
\v 28 K…® ia m…®gei, k…® aremegh ua dikavigh ian faragh Galilin Distrigh…®n mangam.‚Äù  
\v 29 Ez…® Pita kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe bar n…® ateght…® k…®rara puvat…®gham.‚Äù  
\v 30 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®magarir kam…®n n…® uab…® dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim n…® suam, ‚ÄòK…® a g…®fozir puvat…®,‚Äô eght…® tuarim g…®n akazir pumuning damuam.‚Äù  
\v 31 Ez…® Pita akar gavgavimra amua ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® n…® ko ovengs…®va ovengam, k…® bar kamagh…®n m…®kemeghan kogham. Bar puvat…®gham!‚Äù Ez…® suren gumaziba bar kamagh…®ram a m…®gei. 
\s1 Iesus Getsemanin azenim…®n God ko m…®gei 
\r (Matyu 26:36-46 ko Luk 22:39-46) 
\p  
\v 32 Egha Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko temer olivbar azenim, an ziam Getsemanin ghuegha, Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa kagh dapiagh…®v k…®t…® k…® God ko m…®k…®mam.‚Äù  
\v 33 Egha a Pita, Jems ko Jon me inigha ghu. Ez…® atiatim puv…®ram an anadima, a bar osemegha,  
\v 34 kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan navir averiam, os…®mt…®zim a iteragha ghuaghiri. Ez…® k…® aremeghasava ami. Ia kagh ik…®, derav…®ra gan.‚Äù  
\v 35 Egha a mong is…®vagha ghugha, egha uan guam mogh…®n nguazim gir…®gha kamagh…®n God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, tuavir igharazitam ik…®t…®ma God dughiar kurar kam na dam a inigh.  
\v 36 A kamagh…®n God ko m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Ame, nan afeziam, bizitam bar n…®n osemezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n os…®mt…®zir kam, n…® na dam a inigh. K…® ifongezir mogh…®n puvat…®, n…® ifongezir mogh…®ra, n…® damu.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 37 Ez…®ma a uamategha uan suren gumazir pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n bighan ghugha garima me akui. Ez…® a kamagh…®n Pita m…®gei, ‚ÄúSaimon, n…® akui? N…® tong na ko ik…® gan…®va dughiar otevim…®n ikeghan kogham?  
\v 38 Ia na bagh derav…®ra gan, egh God ko m…®k…®m, eght…® os…®mt…®zitam ia damut…®, ia ireghan kogham. K…® fo, ian navir averiaba ifonge, ez…® nivaf…®ziba gavgaviba dar puvat…®. Kamagh…®n pariam ian azi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 39 Egha a uamategha ghugha faragha God ko m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ua a ko m…®gei.  
\v 40 Egha a uamategha suren gumaziba bagha iza gari, me akuav…®ra iti. Pariam puv men azi. Ez…® a me gaghuraz…®, me a m…®k…®mamin akabagh asa. 
\p  
\v 41 Ez…® a dughiar m…®kezim…®n ghugha God ko m…®kemegha uamategha iza me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa avughsava akuav…®ra iti? Arazir kam atakigh! Dughiam oto. Ia gan, Gumazibar Otarim me a is…®va gumazir arazir kurabagh amibar dafarim dar…®ghasa.  
\v 42 Ia d…®kavigh! E mangam! Ia gan. Gumazir na is…®va apanibar an…®ngamra muna izi!‚Äù 
\s1 Judas Iesus isava an apanibar dafarim gat…® 
\r (Matyu 26:47-56 ko Luk 22:47-53 ko Jon 18:3-12) 
\p  
\v 43 Egha Iesus Pita, Jems ko Jon m…®g…®av…®ra itima, Judas, an suren gumazir 12 plan mam oto. Maburan av…®rim a ko m…®dorozir sababa ko asianiba inigha Iesus bagha izi. Ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Judan gumazir dapaniba, me me amangiz…®, me izi.  
\v 44 Gumazir Iesus is…® men dafaribar ar…®ghasava amim faragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® arazir kam ian akagham. Gumazir k…® toramim, kar Iesusra. Ia an suiragh, egh deraghv…®ra an gan…®va, egh a inigh mang…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 45 Ez…® Judas Iesus bagha ghuav…®ra ikia kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa!‚Äù Eghava an tore.  
\v 46 Ez…® gumaziba izava Iesus…®n agharibagh iregha, pamtem an suiki. 
\p  
\v 47 Ez…®ma Iesus…®n borogh…®n itir gumazir mam uan m…®dorozir sabam asigha, ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n kuarim atu, ez…® an kuarim dutuaghir…®.  
\v 48 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® ok…®mak…®ar gumazim puvat…®. Ia tizim bagha nan suighasa m…®dorozir sababa koma asianiba atera izi?  
\v 49 K…® zurara ia ko ikia, God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®riam…®n aven sure gami. Ez…® ia nan suighan aghua. Ez…® God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n osizirim m…®kemezir mogh…®ra ia kamagh…®n na gami.‚Äù  
\v 50 Ez…®ma Iesus…®n suren gumaziba bar aneteghava are. 
\s1 Gumazir igiar mam arav ghu 
\p  
\v 51 Ez…® gumazir igiar mam bizitam aruzir puvat…®, egha inir ghurghurir azenan itimra ikegha Iesus…®n g…®n zui. Ez…® Iesus…®n apaniba an suiraz…®ma,  
\v 52 a uan azenan itir inir ghurghurim ategha bibiamrama arav ghu. 
\s1 Iesus Judan kot…®n aven iti 
\r (Matyu 26:57-68 ko Luk 22:54-55 ko 22:63-71 ko Jon 18:13-14 ko 18:19-24) 
\p  
\v 53 Ez…® Iesus…®n apaniba a inigha ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim bagha ghu. Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judan gumazir dapaniba, ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba, me bar iza uari akufa.  
\v 54 Ez…® Pita mong t…®zim a gat…®gha Iesus…®n g…®n ghua bar ghua ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n d…®penim…®n d…®vazim…®n aven ghu. Egha kagh ganganir gumaziba koma aperaghav ikia avim…®n f…®i. 
\p  
\v 55 Ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba koma Judan kot…®n aven itir gumaziba bar Iesus…®n m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa akar men akurvaziba buri, egha tam batozir puvat…®.  
\v 56 Gumazir av…®riba ifavarir m…®g…®r…®g…®abar Iesus gami, ez…® men m…®g…®r…®g…®aba vorogh…®ra zuir puvat…®.  
\v 57 Ez…® marazi d…®kavigha ifavarir akar kam…®n a m…®gei,  
\v 58 ‚ÄúE orazima, a ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® God…®n D…®penir gumaziba ingarizim anep…®righ, egh dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n igharazitam…®n ingarigham. God…®n D…®penir k…® ingaramim gumaziba ingarizir puvat…®zim.‚Äô‚Äù  
\v 59 Ez…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba uaghan guizbang…®ra vorogh…®ra zuir puvat…®. 
