\v 60 Ez…®ma ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim d…®kavigha men tong…®n tugha egha Iesus…®n azara, ‚ÄúN…® akatam ikarvaghan aghua? Me n…® gasir akar kam, a guizbang…®ra, o?‚Äù  
\v 61 Ez…® Iesus n…®m…®ra ikia men m…®g…®r…®g…®atam ikarazir puvat…®. 
\p Ez…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim uam an azara, ‚ÄúN…® Krais, God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim? N…® gumazamiziba ziam fer God…®n Otarim?‚Äù  
\v 62 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® an Otarimra. Eght…® n…® gant…®, Gumazibar Otarim gavgavim itir God…®n agharir guvim daperagh overiam…®n ghuariaba sara izam.‚Äù  
\v 63 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim uan korotiaba abighava azara, ‚ÄúE tizim bagh ua akar akurvaziba buriam? Markiam!  
\v 64 Ia uari a barasi, a m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kurabar God…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®si. Ez…® ia manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si?‚Äù Ez…® me bar akam a gasa, egha ghaze an aremegham. 
\p  
\v 65 Egha marazi a gipari. Egha me an damaziba avara, egha me uan agharibar a m…®sogha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® m…®k…®m. Tinara n…® m…®sosi?‚Äù Ez…® ganganir gumaziba a inighava a m…®soghav…®ra iti. 
\s1 Pita ghaze, a Iesus g…®fozir puvat…® 
\r (Matyu 26:69-75 ko Luk 22:56-62 ko Jon 18:15-18; 18:25-27) 
\p  
\v 66 Dughiar kamra Pita d…®penim…®n d…®vazim…®n aven vang…®nan itima, ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n ingangarir guivir mam izi.  
\v 67 Egha Pitan garima an avim…®n f…®ima, a d…®k…®rav…®ram an gari. Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uaghan Nasaret…®n gumazir kam, Iesus ko ike.‚Äù  
\v 68 Ez…® a uab…®n ghuaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® n…® m…®geir bizir mam g…®fozir puvat…®.‚Äù Egha d…®vazim…®n tiar akar ekiam…®n otivasa azenan ghu. Ez…® tuarim ati.  
\v 69 Ez…® ingangarir guivir kam kagh an apigha tuivighav itir gumazamiziba ua me m…®gei, ‚ÄúMuna men mav.‚Äù  
\v 70 Ez…® a ua uab…®n ghuara. Ez…® mong g…®n, an borogh…®n tuivighav itir darasi Pita m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Galilin gumazim, kamagh…®n guizbang…®ra n…® men mav…®ra.‚Äù  
\v 71 Ez…® a pamtem m…®g…®a ghaze, K…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, k…® ifaraght…®ma God na gas…®ghasigham. Egha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® gumazir ia m…®geir kam g…®fozir puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 72 A kamagh…®n m…®g…®av…®ra itima tuarim uam ake. Ez…® Pita Iesus a m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®am gin…®r…®, ‚ÄúN…® faragh dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n suam, k…® Iesus g…®fozir puvat…®, eght…® tuarim g…®n dughiar pumuning…®n akegham.‚Äù Egha Pita n…®ghn…®ghava avegha bar puv…®rama azi. 
\c 15  
\s1 Me Iesus inigha Pailat bagha ghu 
\r (Matyu 27:1-2 ko 27:11-14 ko Luk 23:1-5 ko Jon 18:28-38) 
\p  
\v 1 Egha bar m…®zaraghara, ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, ko Judan gumazir dapaniba, ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba, ko Judan kot…®n aven itir gumazir igharaziba sara, me n…®ghn…®zir mam bato. Egha me Iesus…®n dafariba ikegha an akua ghua Pailat gan…®ngi.  
\v 2 Ez…® Pailat an azara, ‚ÄúN…® Judabar Atrivim, o?‚Äù Ez…® Iesus a ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAre, n…® deraghav…®ra m…®gei.‚Äù  
\v 3 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba bizir av…®ribar a m…®g…®ava, a gasi.  
\v 4 Ez…® Pailat uam an azara, ‚ÄúN…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba ikarvagham, o puvat…®? N…® orasi, me bizir av…®riba n…® m…®g…®a n…® gasi.‚Äù  
\v 5 Ez…® Iesus bar m…®geir puvat…®z…®ma, Pailat d…®gavir kuram gami. 
\s1 Pailat ter ighuvim…®n Iesus guasa m…®gei 
\r (Matyu 27:15-26 ko Luk 23:13-25 ko Jon 18:38-19:16) 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Pailat amir arazim kamak…®n, azeniba bar isar ekiar kam…®n dughiam, me Pailat…®n m…®k…®mt…®ma a kalabus…®n itir gumazir me ifongezim, aneteght…®, a mangam.  
\v 7 Gumazir mam, an ziam Barabas, a gumazir gavman ko m…®soziba me ko kalabus…®n iti. Me bizir kam bagha kalabus…®n iti. Me gavman ko uariv sogha gumazir mabav soghez…® me ariagh…®re.  
\v 8 Ez…® gumazamiziba Pailat iti nagh…®n ghuavanabogha kalabus…®n itir gumazir me ifongezim ateghasa Pailat…®n azangs…®si. Kar arazir Pailat zurara amim.  
\v 9 Ez…® Pailat men azara, ‚ÄúK…® Judabar Atrivim ategh ia bagh anemangasa, ia ifonge?‚Äù  
\v 10 Pailat fo, ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba Iesus amir biziba bagha naviba ikuvava, a isa Pailat…®n dafarim gat…®.  
\v 11 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba m…®g…®r…®g…®ar navibagh iniviba gumazamizibagh an…®di. Eght…® me Pailat…®n m…®kemeght…® a Iesus…®n anogoregh, egh Barabas ateght…® a me bagh izam.  
\v 12 Ez…® Pailat azara, ‚ÄúGumazir ia Judabar atrivim ar…®zim, k…® manmagh…®n a damuam?‚Äù  
\v 13 Ez…® gumazamiziba pamtem dia kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúA is…® ter ighuvim…®n aneguragh!‚Äù  
\v 14 Ez…® Pailat men azara, ‚ÄúManmagh su? An arazir kurar manam gami?‚Äù Ez…® me bar pamtem d…®a m…®gei, ‚ÄúTer ighuvim…®n aneguragh!‚Äù  
\v 15 A me damut…® men naviba deraghasa, Pailat Barabas ataki. Egha m…®dorozir gumazibav kemez…® me benibar Iesus fozoroghez…® Pailat ter ighuvim…®n aneguasa me gan…®ngi. 
\s1 M…®dorozir gumaziba Iesus d…®pofi 
\r (Matyu 27:27-31 ko Jon 19:2-3) 
\p  
\v 16 Egha m…®dorozir gumaziba Iesus inigha gavman…®n d…®penir ekiam…®n m…®riam…®n aven ghuaghira m…®dorozir gumaziba bar men diaz…® me iza uari akufa.  
\v 17 Egha me korotiar aghevir ruarim a garugha egha d…®konir amianim ark…®righa an dapanim garu.  
\v 18 Egha me magh…®ra an diava a m…®gei, ‚ÄúJudabar Atrivim, n…®rara atrivir ekiam!‚Äù  
\v 19 Egha me aghorim an dapanim m…®soghava, egha uaghan a giparav…®ra iti. Egha me ifara uan tevir akuribagh is…®n ira mati me guizbang…®ra an ziam fe mogh…®n ami.  
\v 20 Me arazir kabar a gamua a d…®povegha g…®vagha, a da korotiar me a agaghuiziba suegha, ananaba agaghui. Egha me a isa ter ighuvim…®n a gafughasa an akua zui. 
\s1 M…®dorozir gumaziba Iesus isa ter ighuvim…®n aneguragha a gafu 
\r (Matyu 27:32-44 ko Luk 23:26-43 ko Jon 19:17-27) 
\p  
\v 21 Sairinin gumazir mam Saimon, a Aleksander ko Rufus…®n afeziam, a nguibar igharazim…®n ikegha Jerusalem…®n aven zui. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba Iesus guamin ter ighuvim a terasa an suiraz…®, an aneteri. 
\p  
\v 22 Egha me ghua danganir mam…®n ziam Golgata, me an otifi. (Danganir kam…®n ziam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, Dapanir Agharir Danganim.)  
\v 23 Egha me wain ko m…®zaziba agevir d…®pam veregha Iesus gan…®dima an an aghua.  
\v 24-25 Ez…® aruem anaboz…®, me a isa ter ighuvim…®n aneguragha a gafu. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba an korotiaba tuiragh uari dan…®ngasa satu gikararai. Tina faragh otogh, korotiar manam iniam.  
\v 26 Egha me an gun m…®geir akar kam osiri, ‚ÄúA Judabar atrivim.‚Äù Me ghaze, a bizir kam bagha kot…®n tughava areme.  
\v 27-28 Me gumazir ok…®ava m…®dorozibagh amizir pumuning, Iesus…®n borogh…®n uaghan aning agura. Me mav isa Iesus…®n agharir guvim…®n itir ter ighuvim gafu, egha mav isa agharir ik…®riam…®n itir ter ighuvim gafu. 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® iza zui darasi me d…®bovibar a m…®g…®ava uan dapaniba roava ghaze, ‚ÄúOre! N…®, gumazir God…®n D…®penim akarigh aruer pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n uam an ingarasa m…®kemezim,  
\v 30 dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® uab…® uab…®n akuragh, ter ighuvim ategh izighir…®!‚Äù  
\v 31 Ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judan arazibagh fozir gumaziba uaghan kamagh…®ram a d…®pova uariv gei. Me kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúA igharaz darazir akurvagha uab…®ra uab…®n akurvaghan asa!  
\v 32 Gumazir kam, a ghaze, k…® God Ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim ko Israelbar Atrivim, a ter ighuvim ategh izighir…®t…®ma, e an ganigh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikiam.‚Äù Gumazir ok…®mak…®ar an borogh…®n guraghav itimning uaghan m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kurar av…®riba puv…®ram a m…®g…®av…®ra iti. 
\s1 Iesus…®n ovevem 
\r (Matyu 27:45-56 ko Luk 23:44-49 ko Jon 19:28-30) 
\p  
\v 33 Aruem iza pazaghar torim…®n itima m…®tatem nguazim…®n itir nguibaba bar da avaragha, ghua dughiam 3 klogh…®n guarat…®zim…®n tu.  
\v 34 Egha dughiam 3 klogh…®n itima Iesus tiarir ekiam…®n pamtem kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúEloi, Eloi, lama sabaktani?‚Äù Akar kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, Nan God, nan God n…® tizim bagha na ataki?  
\v 35 Ez…® rogh…®ra tuivighav itir darasi oregha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa oragh, a Elaijan dei.‚Äù  
\v 36 Ez…® gumazir mam ivegha ghua d…®pam…®n suizir bizim isa wain…®n afangt…®zim garugha a isa aghorir mam gat…®gha, Iesus damasa an an amadi. Egha a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa tegh, e ganika, Elaija ti iz…®va an akuragham, o puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 37 Ez…® Iesus pamtem diagha duam sue. 
\p  
\v 38 Ez…® God…®n D…®penim…®n itir inir ekiar guraghav itim p…®n ikegha tong…®ra bigha ghuaghira v…®n otogha akuar pumuning ir…®.  
\v 39 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir 100 plan garir gumazir dapanir mam, Iesus…®n borogh…®n tughav ikia orazi a pamtem diagha manmagh…®n aremezir arazim…®n ganigha ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, gumazir kam God…®n Otarimra!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 40 Ez…® amizir maba mong saghon tuivighav ikia gari. Men tong…®n Makdalan nguibam…®n amizim Maria, ko Jems…®n igiam ko Josep…®n amebam Maria, ko Salome.  
\v 41 Amizir kaba Galilin ikegha Iesus…®n akurvagha egha an g…®n arui. Amizir av…®rir maba sara Iesus ko Jerusalem…®n anabogha uaghan iti. 
\s1 Me Iesus…®n kuam isa dag…®ar torim gat…® 
\r (Matyu 27:57-61 ko Luk 23:50-55 ko Jon 19:38-42) 
\p  
\v 42-43 Dat…®r…®gh…®n Sabat bagha bizibar k…®rir dughiam. (Eght…® guarat…®zim Sabat otogham.) Ez…® kamagh…®n aruem gevima, Arimatean gumazim Josep, Judabar kot…®n aven itir gumazir aghuir me bar fozim. A uab…® uaghan God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam bagha m…®zuai. An atiatir puvat…®gha Iesus…®n kuam iniasa ghua Pailat…®n azai.  
\v 44 Ez…® Pailat orazi, Iesus aremegha g…®vaz…®, a d…®gavir kuram gami. Egha a m…®dorozir gumazir 100 plan garir gumazim bagha akam amadaz…®ma a izima an an azara, ‚ÄúIesus guizbang…®ra aremez…®, o?‚Äù  
\v 45 Ez…® an an m…®g…®r…®g…®am baregha a fo, Iesus guizbang…®ram areme. Ez…® a Iesus…®n kuam iniasa Josep…®n amamangat…®.  
\v 46-47 Ez…® Josep inir ghurghurir aghuir mam givezegha izava Iesus…®n kuam adangi. Egha a righa ghua dag…®ar torir me dutuzim…®n ghugha aner…®zima Makdalan amizim Maria ko Josep…®n amebam Maria, aning garima, Josep Iesus…®n kuam isa dag…®ar torim…®n aven anet…®gha, dag…®ar ekiar mam poghpuegha izava an akam dukua. 
\c 16  
\s1 Iesus ua d…®kafi 
\r (Matyu 28:1-8 ko Luk 24:1-12 ko Jon 20:1-10) 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Sabat…®n dughiam g…®vaz…®ma, Makdalan amizim Maria, Jems…®n amebam Maria, ko Salome mang…® Iesus…®n kuam daghuasa borer mughuriar aghuaribagh ivese.  
\v 2-3 7 pla dughiabar faragha zuir dughiam…®n aruem anadima m…®zaraghara me dag…®ar torir matmatiam…®n ghua uarira uariv gei, ‚ÄúTina dag…®ar torim…®n akam gasarazir dag…®am puegham?‚Äù  
\v 4 Egha me ghua garima dag…®ar ekiar kam, me a poghpuegha ghu.  
\v 5 Ez…® me dag…®ar torir akam…®n aven ghua garima gumazir igiar mam korotiar ghurghurir ruarim arugha agharir guvim…®n amadaghan aperaghav iti. Ez…® me an ganigha bar aguaghfa. 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa akongan mark…®. Ia Nasaret…®n gumazim Iesus bagha gari. A ter ighuvim…®n aremegha ua d…®kafi! A kagh itir puvat…®. Ia kagh a ir…®ghav ikezir danganim…®n gan.  
\v 7 Egh ia mang…®, Pita ko an suren gumazir igharazibav kemegh, ‚ÄòA ian faragh Galilin mangam. A m…®kemezir mogh…®n ia munagh a bativam.‚Äô‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…®ma me d…®gavir kuram gamigha aguava azenan ghuegha puv are. Me atiatingi, kamagh…®n me taraziv kemezir puvat…®. 
\s1 Makdalan amizim Maria Iesus…®n gani 
\r (Matyu 28:9-10 ko Jon 20:11-18) 
\p  
\v 9 Iesus 7 pla dughiabar faragha zuir dughiam…®n m…®zaraghara ua d…®kavigha Makdalan amizim Maria faragha uab…® isava an aka. Amizir kamnaghra Iesus faragha duar kurar 7 pla an itiba batoke.\f + \ft (16:9-16) Fofozir gumazir av…®riba Sapta 16, ves 9…®n kegha ghua 20…®n tuzir akabav g…®a ghaze, Mak uab…® an osirizir pu, gumazir mam g…®n an osiri.\f* 
\v 10 Ez…® gumazamizir Iesus ko aruava ikeziba, me a bagha bar osemegha puv azia itima, Maria ghugha Iesus…®n gun me m…®gei.  
\v 11 Ez…® me orazi, Iesus ua d…®kavigha uab…® isa Makdalan Marian akaz…®, an an gani. Me kamagh…®n oregha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim amizir kam…®n akabar itir puvat…®. 
\s1 Suren gumazir pumuning tuavim…®n Iesus…®n gani 
\r (Luk 24:13-35) 
\p  
\v 12 Egha dughiar kamnaghra g…®n Iesus gumazir igharazim…®n m…®n otoz…® suren gumazir pumuning nguibar ekiam…®n azenan zuima an aning bato.  
\v 13 Ez…® aning uamategha iza bizir kam…®n gun maraziv kemez…®, me uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim aning…®n akabar itir puvat…®. 
\s1 Iesus me damuamin ingangarim…®n gun uan suren gumazibav gei 
\r (Matyu 28:16-20 ko Luk 24:36-49 ko Jon 20:19-23) 
\p  
\v 14 Egha g…®n 11 plan suren gumaziba apima Iesus uab…® isa men aka. Egha a, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim puvat…®zir bizim ko, me navir gavgavim ikia a ua d…®kaviz…® m…®g…®r…®g…®am marazi an ganigha m…®geima me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n itir puvat…®, ez…® bizir kaba bagha Iesus me m…®g…®a men atari.  
\v 15 Egha a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúMang…® nguazir kam bar a daruva nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamiziba bar akar aghuim me m…®k…®m.  
\v 16 Eght…® tina n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ik…®va, egh rueght…®, God an akuraght…®, a zurara God ko ikiam. Eght…® tina n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itir puvat…®, a God…®n kot…®n ik…®va ivezir kuram iniam.  
\v 17-18 Eght…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itiba, mirakel…®n arazir kaba uaghan me bativam: me nan ziam duar kuraba batogh…®va, me nguibabar akar fozir puvat…®zibav k…®m…®va, egh kuruziba uan dafaribar dar suigham. Egh me imezir d…®par ariagh…®ritamar ameght…® a tong men navibagh as…®ghasighan kogham. Egh me uan dafariba is…® ar…®mariar gumazibar ar…®ght…® men ar…®mariaba g…®vam.‚Äù 
\s1 God Iesus inigha uan Nguibam…®n ghuavanabo 
\r (Luk 24:50-53 ko Aposel 1:9-11) 
\p  
\v 19 Egha Ekiam Iesus bizir kabar me m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma God a inigha uan nguibam…®n ghuavanabo. Ez…®ma a God…®n agharir guvim…®n amadaghan aperaghav iti.  
\v 20 Ez…®ma an suren gumaziba nguazir kam…®n danganiba bar dar ghuava akam akuri. Ez…® Ekiam me ko ingara uan akam gavgavim a gan…®ga mirakel…®n araziba sara akakasi, kamagh…®n gumazamiziba fo, akar kam guizbang…®ra.